\h 1 Samuel 
\toc3 1SA 
\toc2 1 Samuel 
\toc1 God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Samuel, An Ak…®nafarir Faragha Zuim 
\mt1 God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Samuel, // An Ak…®nafarir Faragha Zuim 
\mt2 O 
\mt1 1 Samuel 
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam, a gumazir dapaniba g…®vazir dughiam…®n otivizir biziba ko, Israelia uari atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n faraghav…®ra otozir bizibagh eghari. Ak…®nafarir kam…®n danganir av…®riba, gumazir 3pla geghari. Samuel uab…® Israelian gumazir dapanir abuananam…®n ike. Ak…®nafarir kam uaghan Atrivim Sol geghari, a Israelian atrivir faraghav…®ram otozim. Ez…® Devit…®n eghaghanir av…®riba uaghan iti, kar, a t…®ghar atrivim…®n otivamin dughiam. 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam, eghaghanir av…®riba iti, da pura eghaghanir k…®niba puvat…®. Samuel…®n ak…®nafarir faragha zuir kam, kamagh…®n en akaghasa, gumazim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ik…®va an apengan ikiam, egh a deraghv…®ra ikiam. Egh an an akaba baraghan kogh, a ikuvigham. E deraghv…®ra akar kam…®n ganam, God a isa Eli gan…®ngi, a 1 Samuel 2:30…®n aven iti. A ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir nan ziam fem, k…® ziar ekiam a dan…®ngam. Gumazir na barazir puvat…®zim, k…® bar aneb…®ragham.‚Äù 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam…®n, n…®ghn…®zir pumuning kamagh…®n iti, Israelia atrivir tam ikiam, o puvat…®gham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God a uab…® guizbang…®ra Israelian atrivim. Ez…® Israelia ghaze, me uari atrivitam ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God me bagha atrivir mam am…®sefe. God uab…® Israelian atriviba ko gumazamiziba, bar mogh…®ra men afeziam, egha a uab…® me gatifa. Atrivim ko gumazamiziba, me God…®n apengan ikiamin dughiam, me deraghv…®ra ikiam. Ez…® gumazamizir an akaba batoziba, me os…®mt…®ziba bativam. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Eli ko Samuel…®n eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 1--7) 
\s1 Elkana uan adarazi ko Silon zui 
\p  
\v 1 Gumazir mam a iti, an ziam Elkana, an Efraim…®n anabam…®n gumazim, an Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®ar doziba itir nguibar ekiam Raman iti. Elkana a Jeroham…®n otarim, ez…® Jeroham a Elihun otarim, Elihu a Tohun otarim, ez…® Tohu a Suf…®n otarim, ez…® Suf a Efraim…®n anabam…®n gumazir mam.  
\v 2 Elkana amuir pumuning iti, Hana ko Penina. Penina boriba bati, ez…® Hana otir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 3 Azeniba bar dar dughiar vam…®ra, Elkana zurara uan nguibam atagh…®ragha Silon nguibam…®n ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim…®n ziam fava ofabagh ami. Dughiar kam…®n, Elin otarimning Hopni ko Finias, aning Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir gumazimning…®n ikia, Silon nguibam…®n itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n iti.  
\v 4 Elkana zurara ofabagh amir dughiam…®n, a zurara as…®zim aghoregh an tuziba ab…®gh dar akuaba is…®, uan amuim Penina ko, otariba ko guiviba vaghvagh me dan…®ngam.  
\v 5 Egha Elkana bar Hana gifongegha, bar an apangkufi. A fo, God an navim apuiz…®, a boriba batir puvat…®. Arazir kam bang…®n, Elkana as…®zir tuzir ekiaba a gan…®di.  
\v 6 Amizir kamning, aning penemning, egha dughiabar aning…®n mav bizibar faragh…®v…®ra mangasava ami. Ez…® Hanan penem a gas…®ghas…®ghasa a d…®pova ghaze, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Hanan navim apuiz…®, Penina os…®mt…®zim an navim dan…®ngasa, akar igharagha gariba ko aghums…®zir akabar Hana gami. 
\p  
\v 7 Azeniba bar Penina arazir kamra Hana gami. Me zurara Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n ghua, Penina akar igharazibar Hana d…®pov a m…®k…®mt…®, a bar pazav…®ra uab…® baragh aziam, kamagh…®n amiz…® a dagheba apir puvat…®.  
\v 8 Ez…® Elkana kamagh…®n an azangs…®si, ‚ÄúHana, n…® tizim bagha azi? N…® tizim bagha dagheba apir puvat…®? Egha tizim bagha navim zuraram osei? Guizbang…®ra, n…® boritam batezir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® fo, n…® bar na gifonge, n…® ti na giz…®n otarir 10pla bateghai, n…® m…®gh…®gha me g…®n…®ghn…®ghan koghai, egha n…® na isa guam dafaghai.‚Äù 
\s1 Hana Eli ko m…®gei 
\p  
\v 9 Dughiar mam…®n me Silon ikia amegha g…®vagha, Hana d…®kavigha ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n azenan an damazim…®n m…®t…®. Dughiar kam…®n ofa gamir gumazim Eli, uan dabirabim inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n azenan, a gaperaghav iti.  
\v 10 Ez…® Hana bar osemegha bar paza uab…® baragha aziava, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt D…®boboniba 6:5\x*Egha Hana akar gavgavim Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko anek…®ra ghaze, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, k…® n…®n ingangarir amizim, n…® nan gan…®va nan apangkuvasa, k…® ifonge. N…® nan os…®mt…®zir kam…®n gan na g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Ga uaning, n…® na bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. Egh n…® otaritam na danight…®, k…® a is…® n…® dan…®ngight…® a n…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n ik…® mang…® uan ovevem batogham. Eght…® bizir kam…®n ababanim bagh, me an dapanir ar…®zim ap…®ran kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Hana dughiar ruarim…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®g…®av…®ra itima, Eli aperaghav ikia Hanan akatorimra gari.  
\v 13 Hana uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n averara m…®gei. Eli an garima, a m…®gei mogh…®n, akam akarava ami, egha a Hanan tiarim barazir puvat…®. Eli ghaze, Hana ti d…®par onganitam amegha ongani.  
\v 14 Egha Eli kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® man dughiam…®n d…®par onganiba apir arazir kam ategham? N…® d…®penir kam ategh mang…®. N…®n onganir arazir kam g…®vaght…®ma, n…® ua iz…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Hana kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, k…® d…®par onganitam amezir puvat…®, bar puvat…®. Nan navim, os…®mt…®zim bar a itaragha uaghirima, k…® bar oseme. Egha k…® uan os…®mt…®zim isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®ga a ko m…®gei.  
\v 16 N…® kamagh…®n na g…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, k…® amizir kuram. Puvat…®. K…® paza uab…® baragha nan n…®ghn…®ziba bar ikufi. K…® arazir kam bagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®geima n…® nan gari.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Eli m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, n…® navir am…®rizim inigh mang…®. Eght…® Israelian God, bizir n…® an azarazim a n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Hana kamagh…®n Eli m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, ga uaning, k…® n…®n ingangarir amizim. K…® kamaghsua, n…® zurara navir aghuim nan ik…®.‚Äù A m…®kemegha g…®vagha ghuava amegha, g…®n uam oseir puvat…®. 
\s1 Hana otarim bategha a isa God gan…®ngi 
\p  
\v 19 Elkana uan amuimning ko boriba, me d…®magarim…®n Silon akuima, am…®nim tiraz…®ma, me m…®zaraghara d…®kavigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe. Me an ziam fegha g…®vagha, uamategha uan d…®penim bagha Raman nguibam…®n ghue. Ez…® Elkana, uan amuim Hana koma akui. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Hanan azangs…®zim gin…®r…®gha a ikara.  
\v 20 Dughiar mong otevim…®n g…®n, Hana navim asegha otarim bate. Egha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azaraz…®ma, a borir kam na gan…®ngi. Ez…® k…® ziam Samuel a gat…®.‚Äù\f + \fr 1:20 \ft Hibrun akam…®n ziar kam, ‚ÄúSamuel,‚Äù an m…®ngarim mong m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kam…®n m…®n ghu, ‚ÄúAzaragh.‚Äù\f* 
\s1 Hana Samuel isa God gan…®di 
\p  
\v 21 Arazir kam…®n g…®n, Elkana ko an d…®penim…®n itir adarasi, Silon nguibam…®n ghu, egha azeniba bar me ofa gami mogh…®n damuasa. Egh a uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko d…®k…®r…®zir akam bagh, ofa damuam.  
\v 22 Ez…® Hana me ko zuir puvat…®gha kamagh…®n uan pam m…®gei, ‚ÄúBorim tong ekevegh g…®vagh otem ateght…®, k…® a inigh Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngam. Eght…® a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Ez…® Elkana kamagh…®n Hana m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mamagh…®n deragh damus…®, n…® nguibamra ik…® mang…®t…® borim otem ategham. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim damight…® a guizbang…®ra otogham, mati a m…®kemez…® mok…®n.‚Äù Ez…® Hana nguibam…®n ikia deraghav…®ra uan borim gamua a geghufi. 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® g…®n borim otem ategha g…®vaz…®, Hana a inigha, bizir kaba sara inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofa damuasa Silon nguibam…®n itir Purirpenim…®n zui. Bizir kaba, bulmakaun apurir igiar, azenir 3pla itim ko, 10 kilogrem plaua ko, beghiar me memen inim…®n isamigha, wain…®n d…®pam a guriz…® a itim. A bizir kaba inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n zui. Dughiar kam…®n, Samuel, otarir agh…®rimra iti, a t…®ghar gumazir igiam…®n otivam.  
\v 25 Me otogha g…®vagha, bulmakaun apurir igiar kam m…®suegha g…®vagha, otarim inigha Eli bagha zui.  
\v 26 Egha Hana kamagh…®n Eli m…®gei, ‚ÄúO, nan gumazir aruam, n…® na g…®foghav…®ra iti, o puvat…®? K…® amizir kam, faragha n…®n borogh…®n kagh tughav ikia Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei.  
\v 27 K…® otarir kam uab…® dan…®ngasa Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®g…®a an azangs…®si, ez…® a nan azangs…®zim ikara.  
\v 28 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® a isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®di. Eght…® an ik…®r…®m…®rim zurara Ikiav…®ra Itir God baghv…®ra ik…® an ingangarim damuam.‚Äù 
\p Egha me dapaniba avigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe. 
\c 2  
\s1 Hana Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1-10 \xt Luk 1:46-55\x*Egha Hana kamagh…®n God ko m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® na gamima, k…® bar akonge. 
\q2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® gavgavim ko ziar ekiam na gan…®ngiz…®, k…® bar akonge. 
\q1 N…® nan akurazir bizim bang…®n, k…® bar akonge. 
\q2 N…® bang…®n k…® uan apanibar ingaravati. 
\q1  
\v 2 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, tav n…®n m…®n, bar zuezir puvat…®. 
\q2 Egha god…®n igharazitam n…®n m…®n itir pu. Bar puvat…®. N…® bar dagh afira. 
\q2 N…® uab…®ra, dag…®ar ekiam…®n m…®n gavgavim ikia e moga en akurvagha e geghufi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 3 ‚ÄúE gumazamiziba, e kamagh…®n deragh fogham, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bizir e amiba, a bar dagh fo, egha a en araziba tuis…®si. 
\q2 Ez…® ia gumazamizir pura tiariba akarava aruava uan ziaba feba, ia arazir kam ategh uan akaba dukuagh. 
\q1  
\v 4 M…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba, God men barir piba ap…®rima, me m…®soghamin gavgaviba puvat…®. 
\q2 Ez…® gumazir gavgaviba puvat…®ziba, a gavgavim me gan…®di. 
\q1  
\v 5 Gumazamizir fom…®ra dagher av…®riba itiba, God dat…®r…®gh…®n me damight…® me dagheba bagh ingar uan ivezim isi mogh…®n da iniam. 
\q2 Ez…® gumazamizir faragha dagheba puvat…®gha m…®tiriamra itiba, God dat…®r…®gh…®n dagher av…®riba me dan…®ngt…® me ua ingaran kogham. 
\q1 Ez…® amizir otir puvat…®zim, God dat…®r…®gh…®n an akuraz…® a borir 7pla bate. 
\q2 Ez…® amizir borir av…®riba itim, an boriba ovengez…® a uab…®ra iti. 
\q1  
\v 6 Ikiav…®ra Itir God gumazamizibav sozima, me ariaghiri. 
\q2 Egha gumazamizir ariaghireziba, a me gamima me uam angam…®ra iti. 
\q1 God gumazamizibagh amima, me Gumazamizir Oveaghuezibar Nguibam…®n uaghiri. 
\q2 Ez…® a me gamima, me ua d…®kafi. 
\q1  
\v 7 Ikiav…®ra Itir God gumazir mabagh amiz…® me biziba puvat…®, 
\q2 egha marazi gamiz…®, me bizir av…®riba iti. 
\q1 A gumazir mabagh amima, men ziaba bar iraghuegha bar v…®n iti. 
\q2 A marazi gamiz…®, me ziar ekiam ikia bar p…®n iti. 
\q1  
\v 8 Nguazir kam…®n suizir bizir gavgaviba da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n biziba, 
\q2 a uab…® bizir kabagh is…®n nguazim…®n ingari. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamizir onganarazibagh amua nguazir m…®nemeniam g…®pogha a gureba, 
\q2 a me ghufa men akurvasi. 
\q1 A me gamima, me uan kantrin gumazir ekiabar otifi, 
\q2 ez…® gumazamiziba ziar ekiam me gan…®di. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, gumazamizir a baghav…®ra itiba a me geghufi. 
\q2 Egha gumazamizir kuraba a me gas…®ghasight…®, me nguibar kurar m…®tatem itim…®n ovegham. 
\q1 E fo, gumazir gavgavir ekiam itim, a bar uan gavgavim…®n ik…®va avegham. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 10 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God uan apaniba bar me gas…®ghasigham. 
\q2 A uan Nguibam…®n ikia arariba dagarvazi mogh…®n a me dagarvasi. 
\q1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God nguazim…®n m…®kebaba bar dar itir gumazamiziba, a bar me akuvagh kotiam…®n men araziba tuis…®gham. 
\q2 Egh a gavgavim is…® uan atrivir a inabazim danigham, 
\q2 eght…® gumazamiziba bar, men tong…®n, atrivir kam ziar ekiam iniam.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 11 Hana Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®kemegha g…®vagha, Elkana ko ua Raman nguibam…®n ghu. Ez…® an otarir dozim Samuel, a Silon ikia ofa gamir gumazim Elin apengan ikia, an akurvagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarim gami. 
\s1 Elin otarimning arazir kuram gami 
\p  
\v 12 Elin otarimning, Hopni ko Finias, aning gumazir bar kuramning. Aning ofa gamir gumazimning, egha aning ghaze, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a pura bizim, egha aning arazir kurar guar av…®rir igharagha garibagh ami.  
\v 13 God fom…®ra ghaze, gumazamiziba ofa inigh iz…® a damigh…®va, egh g…®n ofa gamir gumaziba bagh, as…®zir tuzir otevir taba iniam. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, gumazitam ofa damus…® as…®zitam avight…®, ingangarir gumazim fok…®n atarir 3pla itim inigh izam.  
\v 14 Ingangarir gumazir kam fok…®n pura m…®ner averiam giniv, as…®zir tuzitam b…®ragh…®va, a inigh mang…® ofa gamir gumazim dan…®ngam.  
\v 15 Dughiar mabar, ofa damuasava amir gumazim, a t…®ghar as…®zir ovim adegh avim…®n a tus…® damut…®, ofa gamir gumazir kamning…®n ingangarir gumazim iz…® a gifar…®va an m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúIa ofa gamir gumazimning Finias ko Hopni bagh as…®zir tuzitaba na dan…®ngigh. An avim…®n da tuasa, ia m…®nem…®n avighizir as…®ziba, ana dar aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia as…®zir tuzir avighizir puvat…®ziba a dan…®ng.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Eght…® gumazir ofa damuamim kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúN…® takigh, k…® ofan arazim…®n g…®n mang…®va as…®zim…®n oviba tueght…®, n…® g…®n as…®zir tuzir manam gifuegh a ini,‚Äù ez…® ofa gamir gumazimning…®n ingangarir gumazim ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra na dan…®ngigh. N…® aghuaght…®, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra uab…® tam iniam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Elin otarir kamning ghaze, God…®n ofaba, da pura bizir k…®niba. Egha aning arazir kurabar gumazamizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha inigha izir ofabagh ami. Aning…®n arazir kurar kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God an gari a bar kufi. 
\s1 Samuel Silon iti 
\p  
\v 18 Dughiar kam…®n Samuel uan mugamra ikia ofa gamir gumazim…®n inir ghurghurir aghuim ikegha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir kam gami.  
\v 19 Azeniba vaghvagha an amebam a bagh azenan daghuamin korotiar otevir muziariba isai. Egha amebam ko afeziam aning azenibar zurara ofa damuasa izir dughiam…®n, amebam korotiar otevir muziarir kam isa Samuel gan…®di.  
\v 20 Egha an amebam ko afeziam Eli bagha zuima a deragh aning damuasava God…®n azai. A kamagh…®n Elkana m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God n…®n amuir kam damut…®, a borir igharazitaba batam, eght…® me otarir n…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®ngizim…®n danganim iniam.‚Äù Eli aning m…®kemeght…®, aning uamategh uan nguibam…®n mangam.  
\v 21 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God deragha Hana gamiz…® a borir kabar naviba adava da bate. An otarir 3pla ko guivir pumuning bate. Ez…® Samuel Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ikia an ingangarim gamua n…®m…®ra aghui. 
\s1 Elin otarimning orazir puvat…® 
\p  
\v 22 Dughiar kam…®n Eli bar ghuriz…®ma, dughiar av…®ribar, an otarimning amir arazir kurar av…®riba, a da barasi. A uaghan kamagh…®n orasi, aning uaghan God bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n ingarir amiziba, koma akui.  
\v 23 Kamagh…®n amiz…® a aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua tizim bagha arazir kurar kabagh ami? Gumazamiziba bar iza guan arazibar gun na m…®gei.  
\v 24 Gua nan otarimning, gua arazir kam atakigh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamiziba tintinibar guan arazir kabagh eghari, kar arazir bar kuram.  
\v 25 Gumazitam arazir kuratam gumazir igharazir tam dat…®ght…®, tav a bagh an abuir gumazim…®n m…®n ik…® God…®n azangs…®ght…®, God bizir kam g…®n amadagham. Eght…® tav arazir kuratam Ikiav…®ra Itir God dat…®ght…®, tina an abuir gumazim…®n ik…® an akuragham?‚Äù Dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God aning…®n arazir kuraba bang…®n aning m…®sueght…® aning aremeghasa n…®ghnigha g…®fa. Ez…® Eli kamagh…®n aning m…®kemez…®, God aning…®n dapanimning gamiz…®ma, aning gavgavigha uan afeziam…®n akaba barazir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 26 \x - \xo 2:26 \xt Luk 2:52\x*Dughiar kam…®n Samuel mong uan mugamra itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ko gumazamiziba, bar a gifonge, ez…® men ifongiar kam pamtem…®n d…®kafi. 
\s1 God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, akar mam…®n gun Eli m…®gei 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim g…®n ghua kamagh…®n Eli m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam kamagh…®n iti, ‚ÄòFom…®ra, n…®n inazir afeziam Aron, uan adarazi ko Isipian atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar itima, k…® iza me batogha uan ifongiam…®n gun me m…®keme.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 2:28 \xt Ua Me Ini 28:1-4; Ofa Gami 7:35-36\x*Egha k…® Israelian anababar tong…®n Aron…®n adarazi am…®sefe, me nan ofan ingangarir gumazibar otivasa k…® me am…®sefe. Me ofa damuamin dakozim…®n ingar, egh pauran mughuriar aghuim amadim tu, egh me nan borogh…®n iz…®s…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n korotiar otevir azenan azuim inigh iz…®. K…® uaghan me m…®g…®a ghaze, Israelia ofa damuasa tuezir as…®zir naba me dar am…®.  
\v 29 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia tizim bagha Israelia zurara ofa damuasa k…® me m…®kemezir bizibar ikura? N…®n otarimning, gumazamiziba na bagha inigha izir ofan as…®zir oviba itir aghuibara amasava da isi, aning da apava m…®karziba saram aghungi. Arazir kam…®n n…® aning…®n ziam fegha nan ziam ab…®ra. Manmagh…®n amiz…®, n…® arazir kurar kam gami?‚Äô 
\p  
\v 30 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® akar kam aghurigha ia m…®gei: K…® fom…®ra ian inazir afeziam Aron uan adarazi ko k…® me m…®keme, me zurara nan ofa gamir gumazibar m…®n ingaram. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam giragham. K…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, gumazir nan ziam fem, k…® ziar ekiam a dan…®ngam. Eght…® gumazir na barazir puvat…®zim, k…® bar aneb…®ragham. 
\p  
\v 31 ‚ÄúN…® deragh oragh, k…® g…®n n…®n gavgaviba ko n…®n inazir afeziabar ik…®zim…®n gavgaviba, k…® me atugh me ab…®nigh me gas…®ghasigham, mati gumazim gumazir igharazim…®n agharim atuzir mogh…®n k…® me atugham. Eght…® n…®n ik…®zim…®n aven gumazitam ik…® mang…® ghurighan kogham.  
\v 32 Kamagh…®n, ia zurara ik…® gant…®, k…® bizir aghuiba is…® Israelian igharaz darazi dan…®ngam, ia tam inighan kogham. Zurara zurara, n…®n adarazir gumazitam g…®n bar ghurighan kogham. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 33 Eght…® g…®n, apaniba iz…® n…®n adarazir gumazamiziba bar me m…®sogham, mati gumazim sabam…®n me atuz…® mogh…®n, me gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®n ar…®ghiregham. Eght…® gumazir vam…®ra ik…®va ofa gamir gumazim…®n ingangarim damuam. Bizir kaba an n…®ghn…®zim gas…®ghas…®ght…®, an navim bar osemeght…®, temeriba an damaziba aghuight…®, da okavigham. 
\p  
\v 34 \x - \xo 2:34 \xt 1 Samuel 4:11\x*‚ÄúG…®n n…®n otarimning, Hopni ko Finias, aning dughiar vam…®ran uaghara aremegham. Aning aremeght…® n…® fogham, nan m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba da bar guizbang…®ra.  
\v 35 Egh k…® ua bagh ofa gamir gumazitam am…®seveght…®, a navim nan ik…®va, ingangarir k…® ifongezibara damuam. Egh k…® an ik…®zim damut…®, me zurara nan ofabar amuamin adarazir otivam, eght…® me k…® m…®sevezir atrivim bagh ingaram.  
\v 36 Eght…® n…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazitaba ik…®v…®ra ik…®va, me ofa gamir gumazir kam bagh mang…®va dagheba ko silvan dag…®aba bagh an azangs…®gham. Egh me kamagh…®n ofa gamir gumazim…®n azangam, ‚ÄòN…® en amamangat…®ght…®ma, e ofa gamir gumazim…®n ingangarir tabara amigh, egh e dagher muziarir taba iniam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\c 3  
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Samuel m…®gei 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® otarir igiam Samuel, a Elin apengan ikia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarim gami. Azenir av…®riba ghuez…®ma, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®riba Israelia gan…®ngizir puvat…®. Dughiar vabara a irebam…®n m…®n garir bizibar aven a me m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 2 Dughiar kam…®n Elin damaziba an ikufi, egha k…®ran oveghang…®n da bar okavigham. D…®magarir mam…®n a uan akuir danganim…®n akui.  
\v 3 Ez…® Samuel God…®n Purirpenim…®n ikia, God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam itir danganim gakui. Dughiar kam…®n God…®n D…®penim…®n itir lam a isiav…®ra itima,  
\v 4 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Samuel…®n dei. 
\p Ez…® Samuel ghaze, ‚ÄúAi, k…® kati.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Egha a d…®kavigha ivegha ghua Eli m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® n…® barazima n…® nan dia, ez…® k…® izi.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Eli kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® n…®n diazir puvat…®. N…® ua mang…® uan m…®siam…®n daku.‚Äù Ez…® Samuel uamategha ghuav akui. 
