\v 6 Egha g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God uam an dia, ez…® Samuel ua d…®kavigha ghua Eli m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan diaz…®, k…® izi.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Eli ghaze, ‚ÄúNan otarim, k…® n…®n diazir puvat…®. N…® ua mang…® uan m…®siam…®n daku.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Dughiar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God t…®ghar uan akaba is…® Samuel…®n akagh a ko m…®k…®mam, kamagh…®n amiz…®, Samuel deraghav…®ra God g…®fozir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God namba 3 dughiam…®n ua Samuel…®n dia, ez…® Samuel d…®kavigha ghua Eli m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan diaz…®, k…® izi.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Eli dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir Godra Samuel…®n dei.  
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Eli a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uamategh mang…® uan m…®siam daku, eght…® a ua n…®n diaght…®, n…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, n…® na m…®k…®m, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, k…® kuarim at…®gha n…® barasi.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù Ez…® Samuel Elin akam baregha uamategha uan m…®siam…®n ghugha akui. 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ua iza tugha faragha Samuel…®n diaz…® mogh…®n, uam an d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúSamuel, Samuel.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Samuel ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® na m…®k…®m. K…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, k…® orasi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® deraghv…®ra oragh. K…® k…®ran oveghang…®n, bizitam Israelian tong…®n a damigham. Eght…® me bizir kam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregh, me d…®gavir kuram damigham.  
\v 12 K…® faragha Elin m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, bizir kurabar me damuam.  
\v 13 K…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar mam an iti. An otarimning akar kurabar nan ziam gas…®ghas…®ki, kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® an adarazi paz…®v…®ra me damuva me kuavaremegham. Ez…® Eli uab…® fo, aning arazir kuram gami, ez…® a aning…®n anogoroghezir puvat…®.  
\v 14 Kamagh…®n amiz…® k…® pamtem…®n Elin adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ofan tam men arazir kuram ag…®vaghan kogham. Bar puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Samuel akar kam baregha uan m…®siam…®n akua ghua am…®nim tira. Egha a ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n tiar akam kui. Egha Samuel uan irebam…®n m…®n garir bizim…®n gun, Elin m…®k…®man atiatingi. 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Eli kamagh…®n Samuel…®n dei, ‚ÄúSamuel, nan otarim, n…® iz…®.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Samuel a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, k…® izi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Eli an azara, ‚ÄúGod manmagh…®ra n…® m…®gei? N…® akatam nan mongan mark…®. N…® akatabar ghuaraght…®, k…® God ko m…®k…®mt…®, a bar paz…®v…®ra n…® damigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Samuel Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akaba bar dar gun a m…®keme, egha bizitam an ghuarazir pu. Bar puvat…®. Ez…® Eli oregha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúA uab…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a bizir tizim damuasa ifonge ana damu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Samuel ko itima a gumazir aruam…®n oto. Egha Samuel m…®geir biziba bar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God adagh amiz…® da guizbang…®ra otifi.  
\v 20 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israel…®n nguazim…®n aven itir nguibaba bar, not…®n amadaghan itir Dan…®n anabam…®n nguibam ikegha bar ghua saut…®n amadaghan Berseban nguibam…®n oto, dar gumazamiziba kamagh…®n fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God guizbang…®ra ua bagha akam inigha izir gumazim…®n ingangarim damuasa Samuel am…®sefe.  
\v 21 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, zurara Silon nguibam…®n Samuel bativa uan akaba isa a gan…®di. 
\c 4  
\s1 Filistiaba, God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam ini 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Samuel Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akaba bar dar gun Israelia m…®geima, me kuariba ar…®gha deraghav…®ra an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba barasi. 
\p Dughiar kam…®n, Israelia d…®kavigha Filistiaba ko uariv soghasa ghua, Ebeneser…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n averpenibar ingarigha dar iti. Ez…® Filistiaba, me Afek…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n uari bagha averpenibar ingarigha dar iti.  
\v 2 Egha Filistiaba uan m…®dorozir gumaziba afegha, Israelia ko m…®dorozim fore. M…®dorozir bar ekiam otoz…®, Filistiaba Israelia ab…®nigha men 4,000plan gumazibav m…®soghez…®ma me ariaghire. 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba uamategha uan averpenibar ghuez…®, men gumazir dapaniba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTizim bagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God Filistiaba ataghiz…®, me m…®dorozim…®n e ab…®ni? Aria, e gumazitaba amadaght…® me Silon mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Boksiam inigh iz…®. Egh e m…®dorozim bagh mang…®s…® Boksiar kam sara mang…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God e ko mang…®va en akuraght…®, en apaniba e ab…®nan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Ua Me Ini 25:22\x*Gumazir dapaniba m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, m…®dorozir gumaziba, gumazir maba amadaz…®ma me Silon ghugha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam ini. Boksiar kam gis…®n, ensel…®n bar gavgavir pumuning…®n nedazimning an iti, ez…® a mati Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim…®n atrivir dabirabim. Boksiam inigha izir dughiam…®n, Elin otarimning Hopni ko Finias, aning uaghan gumazir kabar akuragha Boksiam…®n akua izi. 
\p  
\v 5 Me ghua averpenibar otoz…®, Israelia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n ganigha bar akongegha pamtem…®n diava arai, ez…® n…®g…®nir bar ekiam oto.  
\v 6 Filistiaba orazima Israelia pamten diava araima, me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Hibruian averpeniba iti nagh…®n d…®md…®ar munam baragh. Me tizim bagha kamagh…®n pamtem…®n diava arai?‚Äù Egha g…®n Filistiaba kamagh…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am baraki, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam, a men apanibar averpenim…®n izegha g…®fa.  
\v 7 Egha me atiatigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIsraelian aser maba, men averpenibar aven izegha g…®fa. Maia, e dat…®r…®gh…®n kuram iniam. Fom…®ra en apaniba kamagh…®n garir arazir tam…®n e gamizir puvat…®.  
\v 8 Maia! E dat…®r…®gh…®n bar tegham. Tina en akuraght…® aser gavgavir kaba e gas…®ghasighan kogham? Aser kabara, bizir guar av…®rir kuraba Isip…®n kantrin gumazamiziba da amadaz…®ma, me gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ariaghire.  
\v 9 Ez…® mark…®. E tuivigh gavgavigh guiz…®n gumazibar m…®n m…®sogham. Puvat…®ght…®ma, e Hibrubar ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar otivigham, mati me fom…®ra en ingangarir gumazibar ike. Arazir kam bagh e pamtem…®n m…®sogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Filistiaba bar pamtem…®n m…®soghava Israelia ab…®niz…®, Israelia ara uamategha uan nguibabar ghue. Dughiar kam…®n Filistiaba, 30,000plan m…®dorozir gumazibav soghez…® me ariaghire.  
\v 11 Ez…® Elin otarimning me uaghan aning m…®soghez…®, aning areme. Egha me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam ini. 
\s1 Elin ovevem 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazir m…®dorozir gumazir mam, m…®dorozir danganim ategha dughiar kamra ivegha Silon ghu. A m…®dorozim…®n otozir bizibagh n…®ghn…®gha bar oseme, egha uan korotiam abigha nguazim uan dapanim gaghui.  
\v 13 Ez…® Eli Silon nguibam…®n tuavim…®n m…®riam…®n uan dabirabim gaperaghav iti. A pamtem…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam g…®n…®ghn…®gha gara iti. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir kam, m…®dorozir otozim…®n arazim…®n gun gumazamizibagh eghanasa, Silo nguibam…®n aven izi. Ez…® gumazamiziba oregha bar osemegha, pamtem…®n diava arai.  
\v 14-15 Dughiar kam…®n Eli 98plan azeniba ikiava an damazimning bar an okafi. Eli gumazamizibar ararer n…®g…®nim baregha men azara, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha n…®g…®nir kam gami?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir kam ivegha ghua kamagh…®n Eli m…®gei,  
\v 16 ‚ÄúDughiar kamra k…® m…®dorozim…®n danganim ategha ara izi.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Eli an azara, ‚ÄúNan otarim, manmagh…®n ami?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® gumazim kamagh…®n a geghari, ‚ÄúFilistiaba gavgavigha en m…®dorozir gumazir av…®ribav m…®soghez…®ma me ariaghire. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e men ari. Me uaghan n…®n otarimning, Hopni ko Finias m…®soghez…® aning areme. Egha me uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam ini.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Eli God…®n Boksiam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n uan dabirabim…®n ak…®riba mogh…®n ir…®. A namnam sara aghungizir gumazim egha uaghan bar ghuri, kamagh…®n amiz…® a ira uan guriragharim ap…®righa magh…®rama areme. A 40plan azenibar Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n ike. 
\s1 Finias…®n amuim areme 
\p  
\v 19 Dughiar kam…®n Elin asamir guivim, Finias…®n amuim a navim adai, ez…® an otamin dughiam rogh…®ra ize. A m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baraki, Filistiaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam ini, ez…® an ivozir afeziam ko an pam, aning uaghara areme. Ez…® borim batamin m…®zazim otoz…®, a uan pam ko ivozir afeziam aremezir bizir kamning g…®n…®ghn…®gha, bar m…®zazir ekiam isa zuam…®ra borim bate. M…®zazir kaba bar mogh…®ra a gamima a bar aremeghasava ami.  
\v 20 Ez…® amizir an gara itiba, me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® atiatingan mark…®. N…® oragh, n…® otarim bategha g…®fa.‚Äù Ez…® borir kam…®n amebam tong men akatam baraghizir puvat…®gha men akatam ikarazir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 21 An aremeghasa amua ghaze, ‚ÄúE Israelia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n angazangarim ko gavgavim e ataki.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a ziam, Ikabot borim gat…®. Dughiar kam…®n, a uan pam ko uan ivozir afeziam…®n ovevem, ko God…®n Boksiar apaniba inigha ghuzim g…®n…®ghn…®si.\f + \fr 4:21 \ft Hibrun akam…®n ziar kam, ‚ÄúIkabot,‚Äù an m…®ngarim, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®n ghu, ‚ÄúGod…®n gavgavim itir puvat…®.‚Äù\f* 
\p  
\v 22 Egha bizir kam bang…®n, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúApaniba God…®n Boksiam inigha ghu, kamagh…®n amiz…®, God…®n angazangarim ko gavgavim Israelia ataki.‚Äù An abuan kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®vagha, an areme. 
\c 5  
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam Filistian kantrin iti 
\p  
\v 1 Filistiaba God…®n Boksiam inigha d…®kavigha, Ebeneser…®n nguibam ategha Asdot…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.  
\v 2 Me otivigha g…®vagha God…®n Boksiam inigha, me uan asem Dagon…®n ziam fer d…®penim…®n aven ghu. Egha Dagon…®n marvir guar dag…®am…®n ingarizim…®n borogh…®n anet…®.  
\v 3 Egha am…®mzaraghan bar m…®zaraghara, Asdot…®n gumazamiziba osegha d…®kavigha garima, Dagon…®n marvir guam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam…®n borogh…®n ira fuagha guam nguazim m…®soke. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me Dagon inigha uam an danganim…®n anesara.  
\v 4 Me uam akuigha m…®zaraghara ua ghua Dagon…®n d…®penim…®n aven ghua garima, marvir guar kam ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam…®n borogh…®n ir…®. Ez…® Dagon…®n dapanim ko agharimning d…®p…®riaghir…®gha tiar akam…®n borogh…®n ir…®ghav iti. Ez…® an namnamra deraghav…®ra iti.  
\v 5 Dughiar kam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, bizir m…®ngarir kam bang…®n, men ofa gamir gumaziba ko gumazir Dagon…®n ziam feba, me uan Dagon…®n ziam fer d…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n aven mangasa, an dapanim ko agharimning ir…®ghav ikezir danganim d…®ka zuir puvat…®, me a ikiavk…®ragh arui. 
\p  
\v 6 God…®n Boksiam Asdot…®n itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Asdot…®n itir gumazamiziba ko an borogh…®n itir darasi, a m…®zazim me gasa, me gamima me bar atiatingi. Egha okar kurabagh amima da men m…®karzibar otifi.  
\v 7 Asdot…®n itir gumazamiziba os…®mt…®zir kabar ganigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIsraelian God, m…®zazim isa en asem Dagon ko e gan…®di. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e Boksiar kam ateght…® a ua en nguibam…®n ikian kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Egha me Filistiabar gumazir dapaniba bagha akam amadaz…®, me iza uari akufa. Me uari akuvaz…®, Asdot kamagh…®n gumazamizibar azai, ‚ÄúE Israelian God…®n Boksiam manmagh…®n a damuam?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® gumazir dapaniba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitaba a inigh Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® me a gisaghpugha Get…®n ghu, a Filistiabar nguibar ekiar igharazir mam. 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® me Boksiam…®n akua Get…®n ghuz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uaghan nguibar ekiar kam…®n itir gumazamiziba m…®zazim me gasima, me puv…®rama atiati. Egha okar kuraba gumazamiziba gan…®ga bar me gas…®ghas…®ki.  
\v 10 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Getia God…®n Boksiam isa Filistian nguibar ekiar igharazim Ekron…®n anemada. 
\p Boksiam otogha g…®vaz…®, Ekronba pamtem…®n d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAme, e bar ovengasa, me Israelian God…®n Boksiam inigha kagh ize.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Egha me Filistiabar gumazir dapanibar diaz…® me izez…®, me kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúE uari, ia Israelian God…®n Boksiam amadaght…®ma, a ua uan danganimra mang…®. A e ko en adaraziv soght…® e arighireghan kogham.‚Äù Dughiar kam…®n, God m…®zazim me gasima, men av…®rim ariaghire. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, me bar mogh…®ra puv…®ra atiati.  
\v 12 Ez…® okar kuraba gumazamizibar m…®karzibar otivima, men marazi ariagh…®rima, marazi ariaghirezir puvat…®. Egha me uarir akurvaghasa God…®n deima men d…®md…®ar ararem ghua God…®n Nguibam…®n oto. 
\c 6  
\s1 Filistiaba ua God…®n Boksiam amadaz…® a Israel…®n ghu 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam 7plan iak…®nibar Filistian nguazim…®n ike,  
\v 2 ez…® Filistiaba, uan ofa gamir gumaziba ko kukunir gumazibar diaz…® me izima, me kamagh…®n men azai, ‚ÄúE manmagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam damuam? E uam an danganim…®n anemang…®s…®, e manmagh…®ra anemangam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba ko kukunir gumaziba kamagh…®n me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa uamategh Israelian God…®n Boksiam amangasa a? A dera, Egh ia pura anemangan kogham. Ia uan okar kuraba ag…®vs…®, ia os…®mt…®ziba ag…®vamin ofaba amadagh. Ia kamagh…®n damight…®, ian ar…®mariaba ua deragham, eght…® ia fogh suam, e amizir os…®mt…®zir kam bang…®n, God pazav…®ra e gami.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4-5 Ez…® gumazamiziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE os…®mt…®ziba ag…®vamin ofan manmagh…®n garim God dan…®ngam?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba ko kukunir gumaziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE 5plan Filistian gumazir dapaniba iti. E fo, en gumazir dapanir 5pla ko en gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra ar…®mariar ekiar kam iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia gol…®n taba inigh 5plan okar ia bativizibar nedaziba, ko 5plan kuarzir en nguazim gas…®ghas…®zibar nedazibar ingarigh, God…®n Boksiam sara da amadagh. Egh ia Israelian God…®n apengan ik…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, a ti en nguazim ko aseba ko ia sara uam os…®mt…®zir tam e dan…®ngan kogham.  
\v 6 Ia ti Isipian atrivim ko an gumazamiziba fom…®ra God baraghizir puvat…®z…® mogh…®n damuam, o markiam. God bizir kuraba me gan…®ga me gamima, me onganigha Israelia ataghiz…®, me Isip…®n kantri ategha ghue. Ia arazir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh…®va, ak…®rim ragh God gasan mark…®. 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúIa oragh. Ia karis…®n igiatam…®n ingarigh, egh bulmakaun amebar t…®ghar ingangaritam damuamin pumuning inigh, karis…®n kam gikegh. Aning…®n nguzimning t…®ghar otem atagh…®ragham. Egh ia bulmakaun kamning…®n nguzimning inigh bulmakaun d…®vazim…®n mang…® aning at…®gh.  
\v 8 Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam inigh karis gis…®n anet…®gh. Egh ia os…®mt…®ziba ag…®vamin ofan m…®n, gol…®n ingarizir okaba ko kuarziba, da is…® boksiar dozir tam darugh, egh a is…® karis gis…®n God…®n Boksiam borogh…®n dar at…®gh. Egh bulmakaun amebar kamning ateght…®, aning uaning karis geku mang…®.  
\v 9 Egh ia bar deraghv…®ra gan, karis managh…®ra mangam? A Boksiam izezir kantri Betsemes…®n nguibar ekiam…®n mang…®t…®, ia deraghv…®ra fogh suam Israelian God bizir kurar kam e bagha anemada. Karis an mangan koght…® ia fogh suam, God os…®mt…®zir ekiar kam e bagha anemadazir puvat…®. Os…®mt…®zir kam ti puram oto.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® gumazamiziba m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha an g…®n zui. Egha me bulmakaun amebar pumuning inigha karis gike. Egha bulmakauning…®n nguzimning inigha, bulmakaun d…®vazim…®n aven aning at…®.  
\v 11 Egha me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam ko, boksiar dozir okaba ko kuarzibar nedaziba aven itim, aning isa karis gis…®n aning at…®.  
\v 12 Me aning at…®gha g…®vaz…®, bulmakauning biaghat…®gha Betsemes…®n nguibar ekiam…®n zuir tuavim…®n zui. Aning tuavir kam ataghizir pu. Bar puvat…®. Aning diav arava an zui, ez…® 5plan Filistian gumazir dapaniba, karis…®n g…®n ghua Betsemes…®n m…®taghniam…®n tu. 
\s1 God…®n Boksiam, Betsemes ko Kiriat Jearim…®n iti 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Betsemes…®n gumazamiziba danganir zarir mam…®n azenibar ikia, witba aghora iti. Egha me kogha tuavim…®n gara, God…®n Boksiam…®n apigha me bar akonge.  
\v 14-15 Ez…® bulmakauning karis kurugha ghua, Betsemes…®n gumazir mam Josua, an azenim…®n otogha, azenim…®n aven dag…®ar ekiar mam…®n m…®riam…®n tughav iti. Ez…® Livaiba iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam ko boksiar me gol…®n ingarizir nedaziba itim isa, dag…®ar ekiar kam gis…®n da ar…®ki. Ez…® gumazamiziba karis…®n ter araribar dazibar kuegha, bulmakaun amebamning m…®suegha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofa gami, mati ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rizim. Dughiar kamra Betsemesia uaghan, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofan igharazir mabagh ami.  
\v 16 Filistiabar 5plan gumazir dapaniba gari, Israelia bizir kabagh amima, me dughiar kamra uamategha Ekron…®n ghue. 
\p  
\v 17 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Filistiabar os…®mt…®ziba ag…®vasa, me os…®mt…®ziba ag…®vamin ofan m…®n, 5plan gol…®n okar nedaziba amada. Da vaghvagha men nguibar ekiabar ababaniba, dar ziabar kara: Asdot, Gasa, Askelon, Get ko Ekron.  
\v 18 Me kuarzibar nedaziba amada, da vaghvagha men nguibar ekiar d…®vazir gavgaviba itibar ababanim gami. Egha uaghan Filistian gumazir dapaniba garir nguibar dozibar ababanim gami. Ez…® dag…®ar ekiar me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam at…®zim, a Betsemes…®n gumazim Josuan azenim…®n aven ikia kamagh…®ra iti. Dag…®ar kam, a bizir danganir kam…®n otozim…®n ababanim gami.\f + \fr 6:18 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Ez…® me fom…®ra Hibrun akam Grik…®n akam…®n a g…®ra, ez…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam ‚Äúdag…®am,‚Äù Grik…®n akam…®n g…®n ghu.\f* 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Betsemes…®n gumazir 70pla Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam…®n averiam…®n gani. Kamagh…®n amiz…® God me m…®soghez…®, me bar ariaghire. Ez…® nguibar ekiar kam…®n itir 50,000…®n gumazamiziba ghaze, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me gas…®ghas…®ki. Egha me bar pamtem…®n azi.\f + \fr 6:19 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 20 Egha Betsemes…®n itir gumazamiziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a God…®n bar zuezim, tinara an damazim…®n m…®t…®gham? Bar puvat…®gham. A en atart…®ma, en tav bar deragh ikeghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e God…®n Boksiar kam amadaght…®, a igharagh mangam. E managh…®ra anemangam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Egha me Kiriat Jearim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itir gumazamizibav m…®k…®masa gumaziba amadaz…®ma, me ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúFilistiaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam uam an akua en nguibam…®n ize. E kamaghsua ia iz…®va a inigh.‚Äù 
\c 7  
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 7:1 \xt 2 Samuel 6:2-4; 1 Eghaghaniba 13:5-7\x*Ez…® Kiriat Jearim…®n gumazamiziba iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam inigha ghua, m…®ghs…®ar muziarim…®n p…®n, gumazim Abinadap…®n d…®penim…®n anet…®. Egha me an otarim Eleasar Boksiam…®n ganasa anem…®sefe. 
\s1 Samuel kantri Israel gatifa 
\p  
\v 2 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Boksiam, 20plan azenibar Kiriat Jearim…®n ikez…®ma, Israelia uarir akurvaghasa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n diava azi, egha a baghav…®ra iti.  
\v 3 Ez…® Samuel g…®n kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa guizbang…®ra navibagh iragh ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ua iz…®s…®, ia ik…®zir igharazibar aseba ko aser amizim Astarten nedazim batokegh. Egh ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar an apengan ik…®va, a bagh…®va teviba ap…®r. Eght…® a ian akuragh Filistiaba batueght…® me ua ia gativaghan kogham.‚Äù  
\v 4 Israelia Samuel…®n akam baregha, aser Balba, ko aser amizim Astarten nedaziba batuegha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziamra fe. 
\p  
\v 5 Egha Samuel g…®n Israelia bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúIa iz…®va Mispan nguibar ekiam…®n uari akuvaght…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian akurvaghs…®, k…® a ko m…®k…®mam.‚Äù  
\v 6 Ez…® gumazamiziba bar iza Mispan uari akufa. Me mozir d…®pam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofan m…®n, an d…®pam tuava nguazim ginge. Egha dagheba tagha ikia ghua aruem iraghu. 
\p Egha me kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®gei, ‚ÄúE n…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram gami.‚Äù Ez…® Samuel Mispan Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir dapanim…®n ikia, men kotiaba baragha men m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ak…®ri. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Filistiaba kamagh…®n oraki, Israelia Mispan uari akufa. Ez…® men 5plan gumazir dapaniba uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha Israelia m…®soghasa Mispan izi. Ez…® Israelia orazi, Filistiaba izima me atiati.  
\v 8 Egha Israelia Samuel m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® pamtem…®n ingar Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, a ko m…®k…®m. A en akuraght…® Filistiaba e gas…®ghasighan kogham. N…® a ko m…®geir arazim atagh…®raghan mark…®.‚Äù  
\v 9 Ez…® Samuel sipsip…®n igiar mam m…®suegha, ofan m…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha a tuaz…® a bar isia m…®gh…®ri. Egha Samuel Israelian akurvaghasa pamtem…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®geima, an a baregha men akura. 
\p  
\v 10 Samuel ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim gamuav…®ra itima, Filistiaba m…®dorozim forasa rogh…®ra ize. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Filistiabagh is…®n, overiam…®n ararim gamiz…®, a bar pamtem dagaraz…®, men n…®ghn…®ziba onganiz…® me tintinibar arima, Israelia men gani.  
\v 11 Egha Israelian gumaziba Mispa ategha, Filistiabar ag…®ragha tuavim…®n men av…®rim m…®sozi me ariaghire, egha me ghua Betkar…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n oto. 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Samuel g…®n dag…®ar ekiar mam inigha Mispa ko Sen…®n nguibamning…®n t…®zim…®n anesara. Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDag…®ar kam, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ababanim, a en akuragha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tu.‚Äù Egha ziar kam a gat…®, ‚ÄúDag…®ar Akurvazim.‚Äù  
\v 13 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God Filistiaba bar me ab…®ra, dughiar kam…®n, Samuel Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bizir kabagh ami. A Filistiabar tuaviba ap…®rima me ua iza Israel…®n nguazim…®n aven m…®sozir puvat…®.  
\v 14 Fom…®ra Filistiaba Israelian nguibar ekiamning Ekron ko Get…®n t…®zim…®n itir nguibaba ini, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n me ua da isa Israelia gan…®ngi. Filistiaba ua Israelian nguazir otevitam gativazir puvat…®. Israelia uaghan ua Amoria ko uariv sozir puvat…®gha, uari inigha derav…®ram apia. 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Samuel Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n ikia ghuava areme.  
\v 16 Azeniba bar Samuel nguibar ekiar kabar zui, Betel, Gilgal ko Mispa, a ghua Israelian kotiaba baragha men os…®mt…®ziba ak…®ri.  
\v 17 A nguibar kabar ingangarim ag…®vagh, uamategh uan nguibam Raman mangam. A uaghan nguibar kam…®n kotiaba barasi. Egha uaghan Raman Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofa gamir dakozir mam…®n ingari. 
\c 8  
\ms1 Sol Israelian atrivim…®n oto 
\mr (Sapta 8--15) 
\s1 Israelia uari bagha atriviba buri 
\p  
\v 1 Samuel ghurizir dughiam…®n, a uan otarir pumuning Israelian gumazir dapanimning…®n ikiasa aning am…®sefe.  
\v 2 An otarir ekiam…®n ziam, Joel, ez…® dozim…®n ziam, Abiya. Aning Berseban ikiava, gumazamizibar kotiaba baragha men os…®mt…®ziba ak…®ri.  
\v 3 Egha aning uan afeziam…®n arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Puvat…®. Aning dag…®aba iniasa bar kufi, egha aning gumazir mabar amamangat…®z…®, me uari bagha n…®ghn…®gha dag…®aba isa aning gan…®dima, aning men kotiabar ghuangs…®gha deragha dar k…®rir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 4 Aning…®n arazir kam bang…®n, Israelian gumazir dapaniba uari akuvagha Samuel…®n ganasa Raman nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 8:5 \xt God…®n Araziba 17:14; 1 Samuel 8:19-20\x*Me ghuegha kamagh…®n Samuel m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh. N…® ghurigha g…®vaz…®ma n…®n otarimning n…®n arazir aghuibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. E kamaghsua, n…® e bagh gumazitam am…®seveght…®, a en atrivim…®n ik…®va e geghuvam. E kantrin igharazibar m…®n otivasa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Samuel men azangs…®zir me uari bagha atrivir tam am…®s…®vasa an azarazir azangs…®zir kam g…®n…®ghn…®zima, an an n…®ghn…®zim…®n derazir puvat…®, ez…® a uab…®n m…®k…®masava Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azai, a manmagh…®n damuam.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 8:7 \xt 1 Samuel 10:19; 12:17-19; Hosea 13:10-11\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúBizir gumazamiziba uari bagha n…®ghn…®gha n…®n azangs…®zir kaba, n…® me baragh dar amu. N…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, me n…®n aghuagha n…® batosi. Puvat…®. K…® men atrivim…®n ikian me aghuagha na batosi.  
\v 8 N…® deragh oragh. Dughiar k…® Isip…®n kantrin me inigha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, me ak…®rim na gasaragha asebar ziaba fe. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n me uaghan ak…®rim ragha n…® gasara.  
\v 9 Ez…® k…® kamaghsua, n…® men akam baregh me bagh atrivir tam am…®sefegh. N…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim me dan…®ng suam, ia bar deraghv…®ra bizir ia azarazim bagh n…®ghn…®gh. Egh atrivim damuamin araziba n…® bar derav…®ra dar gun me geghanigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Samuel gumazir me uari bagh atrivitam am…®s…®vasa azaraziba bagha ghugha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me m…®k…®masa m…®kemezir bizibar gun me m…®gei.  
\v 11 Ez…® Samuel kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan atrivim otogh…®va, a bizir kabar ia damuam. A ian otaribar amut…®, me m…®dorozir gumazibar otivam. Eght…® m…®dorozim…®n dughiam…®n, tarazi m…®soghamin karisbar tuivight…®, tarazi m…®soghamin hoziabar dapiagham. Eght…® gumazitaba ingangarir kam damuam, atrivim uan karis inigh managh mang…®s…®, me faragh ivemaram.  
\v 12 A gumazitabar amut…® me 1,000plan m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim…®n ik…®t…®, tarazi 50plan m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim ikiam. Eght…® ian otarir taba an azenim bagh nguazim ab…®ght…®, tarazi an azenim…®n dagher and…®ziba iniam. Eght…® tarazi m…®soghamin bizibar ingar…®va, karis…®n biziba sara ingaram.  
\v 13 Atrivim ian guiviba inight…® me a bagh sandabar ingar, uaghan bretba ko dagher igharazibar an d…®penim…®n da tuam.  
\v 14 Egh a, dagher bar dirir ian azenibar itiba, ko wain…®n azeniba ko oliv…®n azeniba, dar dagher aghuiba is…®, uan ingangarir gumazir dapanibar an…®ngam.  
\v 15 Ia uaghan wain…®n ov…®ziba ko wit…®n ov…®ziba is…® 10plan pozibar dar ar…®gh, egh dar pozir vam…®ra is…® a dan…®ng. Eght…® a dagher kaba is…® uan ingangarir gumazir dapaniba ko an ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar an…®ngam.  
\v 16 Atrivim uan ingangaribar amus…®, ian ingangarir gumaziba ko ingangarir amiziba inigham, a ian gumazir igiar bar aghuiba ko donkiba sara iniam.  
\v 17 Egh a ian 10plan sipsipbar tong…®n sipsip…®n vam…®ra iniam. Egh ia damut…®, ia an ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n ikiam.  
\v 18 Atrivir ia uari uari bagha m…®sevezir kam otogh…®va, arazir kabar ia damut…®ma, ia atrivim basemegh atar…®va m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribar amuva Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n m…®k…®mam. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a bar ia bareghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® gumazamizir kaba Samuel…®n akaba baraghan aghuagha, kamagh…®n a m…®gei ‚ÄúE aghua. N…® e bagh atrivir tam am…®sefegh.  
\v 20 E kantrin igharazibar m…®n otivasa, eght…® en atrivim e gativagham. Egh e uan apanibav soghs…® mangamin dughiam…®n, a en m…®dorozir gumazibagh ativagh men faragh mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® Samuel gumazamizir kabar m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baregha ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®gei.  
\v 22 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Samuel m…®gei, ‚ÄúAria, n…® men akam baregh me bagh atrivitam am…®sefegh.‚Äù 
\p Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, Samuel ghua kamagh…®n Israelian gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa bar mogh…®ra uan nguibabar mang…®.‚Äù 
\c 9  
\s1 Sol Samuel bato 
\p  
\v 1 Gumazir mam Benjamin…®n anabam…®n aven iti, an ziam Kis. An Abiel…®n otarim, ez…® Abiel Seror…®n otarim, ez…® Seror Bekorat…®n otarim, ez…® Bekorat Afian otarim. Kis m…®dorozibagh amir gumazir gavgavim, egha gumazir igharazibar tong…®n ziam ti.  
\v 2 Egha an otarir mam iti, an ziam Sol. Sol gumazir igiar ruarir dirir gavgavim, ez…® Israelian gumazitam an m…®n ruarazir puvat…®. An ganganiba uaghan bar deraz…®, a Israelian igharaz darazigh afira. 
\p  
\v 3 Dughiar mam…®n, Sol…®n afeziam Kis…®n donkin maba tintinibar ghuegha ovenge. Ez…® Kis kamagh…®n Sol m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ingangarir gumazitam inigh gua mang…® donkiba buri.‚Äù  
\v 4 Ez…® aning d…®kavigha Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar ghu, egha Salisan nguazir otevir mam…®n ghugha dar apizir puvat…®. Aning uaghan Salim…®n nguazim…®n ghugha donkibar apizir puvat…®. Egha aning g…®n Benjamin…®n nguazim…®n ghugha, donkibar apizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 5 Aning tagha Suf…®n nguzim…®n ghua otogha g…®vagha, Sol kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazim m…®gei, ‚ÄúAria, ga uamategh uan nguibam…®n mangam. Puvat…®ght…®, gan afeziam ga g…®n…®ghn…®gh pamtem n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar amuva uan donkiba g…®namadagham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® ingangarir gumazim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa, tong orarkegham. Gumazir mam Suf…®n nguibam…®n ikia God…®n akam akura iti. A m…®geir akaba da guizbang…®ram otifi. Ez…® gumazamiziba ziar ekiam a gan…®di. Ga mang…® an ganika, a ti tuavir ga mangamim…®n gun ga m…®k…®mam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n ingangarir gumazim m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa a bagh mangam. Egh ga bizir aghuir manatam inigh mang…® a dan…®ngam? Gan m…®taribar itir dagheba g…®fa, dagher natam itir puvat…®.‚Äù 
