\v 9 (Fom…®ra, God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, Israelia kamagh…®n me d…®bori, ‚ÄúKukunir gumaziba.‚Äù Eght…® gumazitaba bizitam bagh God…®n azangs…®ghs…®, kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúE kukunir gumazim…®n ganasa.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Sol kukunir gumazim bagha azai.) 
