\p  
\v 24 Ez…® isair gumazim as…®zir suer tuzir aghuiba itim asigha p…®n anekagha ghua Sol…®n guam…®n anet…®. Ez…® Samuel ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® gan, kar as…®zir n…® bagha at…®zim, n…® anem…®. God faragha na m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n e ko isar kam…®n ik…® damam, ez…® k…® gumazir kabar diagha, as…®zir kam n…® bagha anet…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® anem…®.‚Äù Ez…® Sol dughiar kam…®n Samuel koma api. 
