\p  
\v 26 Ez…® Samuel bar m…®zaraghara osegha avughsir danganim…®n Sol…®n d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kafigh. K…® n…® amadaght…®ma n…® uan nguibam…®n mangam.‚Äù Ez…® Samuel d…®kavigha izaghira a ko tuavim…®n zuima, Sol…®n ingangarir gumazim uaghan aning ko zui. 
\p  
\v 27 Me nguibar ekiam…®n m…®taghniam…®n borogh…®n ghua, Samuel kamagh…®n Sol m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan ingangarir gumazim amadaght…®ma a faragh mang…®. Eght…® n…® tong na ko ik…®t…®, k…® God m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®abar gun n…® m…®k…®mam. Ez…® an ingangarir gumazim faragha ghu.‚Äù 
\c 10  
\p  
\v 1 Egha Samuel oliv…®n borem itir m…®sevir dozim inigha, an dapanim gingegha an tore. Egha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God n…® ginabagha ghaze, N…® nan gumazamiziba, Israelian atrivim…®n ikiam. N…® me gativagh men akurvagh me okarizir apanibar gavgavim da ua me iniam. Eght…® ababanir tam, n…®n akakagh suam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ua bagha inabazir gumazamizibagh ativaghasa, n…® ginaba. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ababanir kam…®n ganam.\f + \fr 10:1 \ft Bar fom…®ra gumaziba Hibrun akam…®n Grik…®n akam giragha, kagh m…®g…®r…®g…®am gamiz…® a mong ruara. Ez…® e fozir puvat…®, me m…®g…®r…®g…®am kagh uari anet…®, o a ti fom…®ra uaghan Hibrun akam…®n iti, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n ua itir puvat…®. Men Grik…®n akam kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúEgh n…® me gativagh men akurvaght…® apaniba me gas…®ghasighan kogham. Ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir n…® bativamibar n…® m…®k…®masa. Eght…® n…® bizir otivamin kabar gan fogh suam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God gumazamizir kabagh ativagh men ganasa n…® am…®sefe. Bizir kaba da kamak…®n.‚Äù\f* 
\v 2 \x - \xo 10:2 \xt Jenesis 35:19\x*N…® na ategh mang…®va, Benjamin…®n nguazim…®n m…®taghniam…®n, Selsan nguibam…®n, me Resel afazir dag…®ar mozim…®n borogh…®n gumazir pumuning batogham. Eght…® aning donkin n…® ruiagha aruibar gun n…® m…®k…®m suam, me dar api, ez…® n…®n afeziam dagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, a n…® g…®n…®ghn…®gha azangs…®ghav…®ra ikia ghaze, k…® manmagh…®n uan otarim damuam. 
\p  
\v 3 ‚ÄúEgh n…® tuavim…®n mang…®, Tabor…®n nguibam…®n itir temer ekiam…®n otogham. Eght…® gumazir 3pla Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofa damus…® Betel…®n mang…®s…® iz…® temer kam…®n n…® batogham. Men faraghav…®ra izamim, a memen 3pla inigh izam, eght…® tav bret…®n 3pla inigh izam, eght…® abuananam wain…®n d…®pam aven itir memen inim…®n isamizir m…®sevim inigh izam.  
\v 4 Gumazir kaba dughiam n…® dan…®ng…®va bret…®n pumuning n…® dan…®ngam, eght…® n…® aning inigh. 
\p  
\v 5 ‚ÄúEght…® n…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n Gibean nguibam…®n mang…® gant…®, Filistiabar m…®dorozir gumaziba danganir kam…®n ikiam. Egh n…® nguibar ekiam…®n m…®riam…®n mang…®, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir okoruam…®n gant…®, me God…®n ziam fer danganim ategh izighiram. Men tarazi faragh mang…® gitaba ko tambarinbav sogh…®va marvibagh iviam. Eght…® tarazi God…®n akam pamtem an gun m…®k…®m…®va d…®m…®va igh…® izam.  
\v 6 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Duam zuam…®ra n…® giz…®vaght…®, n…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba ko God…®n akam pamtem an gun m…®k…®m…®va igh…® izam. Egh n…® igharagha garir gumazim…®n otogham.  
\v 7 Bizir kaba n…® bativt…®, God n…® ko ikiam. Kamagh amiz…®, n…® damuasa n…®ghn…®zir biziba n…® dar amu. 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúN…® faragh Gilgal…®n mang…®, 7plan dughiabar ik…® na m…®zuam, eght…® k…® iz…® ofan bar isi m…®gh…®ramiba ko, God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofabar amuam. Egh k…® n…® damuamin bizibar, gun n…® m…®k…®mt…®, n…® dar amuam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Sol Samuel ategha ragh…®r…®gha, mangasava amir dughiam…®n, God navir igiam Sol gat…®. Ez…® bizir Samuel m…®kemeziba dughiar kamra bar a batifi.  
\v 10 Ez…® Sol uan ingarir gumazim ko Gibean otoz…®, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir okoruar mam a bato. Bar zuam…®ra God…®n Duam a giz…®vaz…®, a me koma Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n m…®n diava God…®n akam pamtem an gun m…®g…®a ighiagha rui.  
\v 11 Ez…® gumazamizir fom…®ra a g…®foziba, kamagh…®n an gara uarir azangs…®si, ‚ÄúBizir tizim Kis…®n otarim Sol bato? A ti uaghan God…®n akabar gun m…®geir gumazim, o?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 10:12 \xt 1 Samuel 19:23-24\x*Ez…® kagh itir gumazir mam kamagh…®n azai, n…® manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúGod…®n akabar gun m…®geir gumazir kaba, men afeziaba manmagh…®n garir gumaziba? Ez…® azangs…®zir kam ikiav…®ra ikia ghu dat…®r…®gh…®n aghuzir m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n m…®n oto: ‚ÄòSol ti guizbang…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar tong…®n iti, o?‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù  
\v 13 Ez…® Sol God…®n akam…®n gun m…®kemegha g…®vagha, God…®n ziam fer danganim…®n ghuavanabo. 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Sol…®n afeziar dozim, a Sol uan ingangarir gumazim ko aning…®n azara, ‚ÄúGua managh ghugha izi?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Sol ghaze, ‚ÄúGa donkiba buriasa ghua dar apizir puvat…®gha, magh…®ra Samuel bagha ghu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Sol…®n afeziar dozim ghaze, ‚ÄúGa uaning, n…® na m…®k…®m, Samuel tizibar n…® m…®keme?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Sol a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA kamagh…®n ga m…®keme, gumazir maba donkiba bato.‚Äù Egha Sol atrivim…®n ikiasa Samuel a ginabazir bizim…®n gun uan afeziar dozim…®n m…®kezir puvat…®. 
\s1 Sol atrivim…®n oto 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Samuel Israelian gumazamiziba bar men diaz…®, me iza Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n Mispan nguibar ekiam…®n uari akufa.  
\v 18 Me uari akuvagha g…®vaz…®, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God a Israelian God, a ghaze, a Isip…®n ia inigha ian akua kagh ize. A Isipia ko gumazamizir igharazir pazav…®ra ia gamibar, dafaribar ua ia ini.  
\v 19 Ez…® ia dughiar kurabar aven itima God…®n ian akurazir kam, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n ak…®rim ragha a gasara. Egha ia kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ia kamaghsua, an atrivitam ia dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n iz…® uan anababa ko ik…®zibar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n tuifigh, eght…® a ia bagh atrivitam am…®s…®vam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Egha Samuel Israelian anababa vaghvagha bar me inigha iza, satu gikararang…®va Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ifongiam g…®foghamin arazim gamua, egha Benjamin…®n anabam am…®sefe.  
\v 21 Egha Samuel Benjamin…®n anabam…®n itir ik…®ziba inigha iza, vaghvagha men ik…®ziba gara satu gikararava, Matrin ik…®zim am…®sefe, egha Matrin ik…®zim bagha, satu gikararava, Sol am…®sefe, a Kis…®n otarim. Ez…® me a buriava an apizir puvat…®.  
\v 22 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma me ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azara, ‚ÄúGumazir kam, a kagh izava otoz, o puvat…®?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, a muna bizir pozir ekiabar tong…®n modo.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Me akar kam baregha ivemara ghua Sol inigha iza uarir tong…®n anet…®z…®, a uan suemning…®n tugha me gafiragha bar ruara.  
\v 24 Ez…® Samuel gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazir kam…®n gan, kar gumazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God inabazim. Tav uam en tong…®n an m…®n itir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® gumazamiziba bar pamtem…®n d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA en atrivim, a dughiar ruarim…®n ikiamin atrivim!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® gumazamiziba uan atrivim damuamin araziba ko atrivim uab…® damuamin araziba, Samuel adar gun me m…®gei, egha ak…®nafarim…®n da osiri. Egha ak…®nafarim isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n God…®n damazim…®n anet…®. Egha gumazamiziba bar me amadaz…®ma, me uamategha uan nguibabar ghue. 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® Sol uaghan uan nguibam Gibean ghu. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir maba, God men navibagh iraz…®, me uaghan Sol…®n g…®n ghue.  
\v 27 Ez…® gumazir akaba batozir maba kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam manmagh…®n en akuragham?‚Äù Egha me bar Sol…®n aghuagha, bizir aghuitaba a dan…®ngan aghua. Ez…® Sol akatam me ikarazir puvat…®. 
\c 11  
\s1 Sol Amonia m…®sogha me ab…®ni 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Amonian Atrivim Nahas, g…®n uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha Israel…®n itir Distrik Gileat…®n aven ize. Nahas…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba Jabes…®n nguibar ekiam koro, kamagh amiz…®ma Jabes…®n gumazamiziba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® m…®g…®r…®g…®atam e ko anek…®right…®, e n…®n apengan ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 2 Ez…® Nahas kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTuavir bar vam…®ra k…® ia ko akam ak…®ram. Ia Jabes…®n itir darasi, k…® bar ian damazir agharir guvim…®n itiba asigham, eght…® arazir kam aghums…®zim ia ko Israelian igharaziba bar me dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Jabes…®n gumazir dapaniba akar kam baregha kamagh…®n Nahas m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® dughiar 7pla e danight…®, e gumazitaba amadaght…® me Israelian ik…®ziba bar men azaraght…®ma, me ti iz…® en akuragham. Eght…® gumazir en akurvaghamiba puvat…®ght…®, e uari is…® n…® dan…®ng…®va n…®n apengan ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 4 Ez…® akam inigha zuir gumaziba ghua Gibean nguibar ekiam…®n oto, kar Sol…®n nguibar ekiar a itim. Egha me, me gegharima, gumazamiziba bar puv…®rama azi. 
\p  
\v 5 Dughiar kam…®n Sol uan obarir azenim…®n ingarigha g…®vagha, bulmakaun azenim…®n ingariziba inigha iza, gumazamizibar azirakam barasi. A nguibam…®n izegha g…®vagha men azai, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha bar mogh…®rama azi?‚Äù Ez…® me Jabesia amadazir akaba bar dar gun a geghari.  
\v 6 Sol akar kaba baregha g…®vaz…®, God…®n Duam zuam…®ra a giz…®vagha pamtem…®n an ingarima, an atara navim bar oseme. 
\p  
\v 7 Egha a bulmakaun pumuning inigha aning m…®suegha, aning…®n as…®zir tuziba aghoregha, as…®zir tuzir kaba isava gumazir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba inigha izibagh an…®ngi. Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ia as…®zir tuzir kaba inigh mang…® Israelian gumazamizibar ik…®ziba bar men akakagh. Egha akar kam akunasa me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir manam Sol ko Samuel…®n akuragh Amonia m…®sueghan koght…®, Sol gumazir kam…®n bulmakaubav suegh…®va, as…®zir tuzir kabar m…®n dar ghoram.‚Äù Gumazamiziba akar kam baregha g…®vaz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me gamiz…®ma me bar atiatigha d…®kavigha izi. Me bar navir vam…®ran ikia, uari akuvagha, gumazir gavgavir mam…®n m…®n otogha izi.  
\v 8 Egha Sol gumaziba bar me m…®kemez…®ma, me Besek…®n nguibar ekiam…®n uari akuvaz…®, a Israelia d…®borima me 300,000…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, ez…® Judan m…®dorozir gumazibar d…®bobonim 30,000. 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir kaba, kamagh…®n Jabesian akam inigha izir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa ua Jabes…®n mang…® kamagh…®n uan gumazamizibav m…®k…®m: E gurum…®n aruem…®n, iz…® ian akuragh ian apanibar g…®nt…®gham.‚Äù Ez…® Jabesian akam inigha izir gumazir kaba ghua akar kam…®n gun uan gumazamizibav geima, me oregha bar akonge. 
\p  
\v 10 Egha me Nahas m…®gei, ‚ÄúE gurum…®n n…® bagh izam, n…® bizir tizim…®n e damus…® n…® a damu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Bar m…®zaraghara am…®nim t…®ghar tiam, Sol uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ik…®zir 3plan me ab…®ki, ez…® am…®nim itima me ivemara ghua Amonia m…®sosi. Me puv…®ra men av…®ribav sozima me ariaghira ghua aruer ar…®zim…®n tu. Ez…® Amonian gumazir ariaghirezir puvat…®zir varazira, me tintinibar aregha vaghvagha iti. 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Israelia g…®n kamagh…®n Samuel…®n azara, ‚ÄúEn akar gumazir manaba ghaze, Sol en atrivim…®n ikian kogham? N…® en m…®kemeght…®ma, e me m…®sueght…®ma me ar…®m…®ghiregham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Sol men akam baregha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. Dughiar kamra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God e Israelia a en apanibar agharim…®n e ini. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e dughiar kam…®n uan akar gumazitam m…®sueght…® an aremeghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Sol m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, Samuel kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúE Gilgal…®n nguibar ekiam…®n mang…® uam akam ak…®righ kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, Sol en atrivim…®n ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me bar Gilgal…®n ghuegha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n me kamagh…®n akam ak…®ra ghaze, ‚ÄúSol a en atrivim.‚Äù Egha me God…®n damazim…®n ikia God ko navir vam…®ran ikiasa ofabagh ami. Ez…® Sol Israelia ko, me bizir kam bagha bar akonge. 
\c 12  
\s1 Samuel akar abuananam Israelia m…®k…®ri 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Samuel g…®n kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa oragh, ia bizir av…®riba bagha nan azangs…®zima, k…® ia baregha, atrivir mam ia gativaghasa ia gan…®ngi.  
\v 2 Ia gan! Atrivir kam, nan danganim inigh ia is…® tuavir aghuim…®n ia amangam. K…® uab…® ghurigha dapanir ar…®zir ghurghuriba na batifi, ez…® nan otariba ekevegha ia ko iti. K…® fom…®ra uan igiamra ikia ian gumazir dapanim…®n ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tu.  
\v 3 K…® uab…® k…®r kara. Ia bar deragha nan arazibagh fo. K…® arazir kuratam ia damight…®, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko atrivir a ia bagha inabazim…®n damazim…®n, nan gun m…®k…®m. K…® ti gumazitam…®n bulmakaun tam o donkin tam ini, o? K…® ti tav gifaragha an biziba okeme, o? K…® ti tav pazava a gami, a? K…® ti gumazitam…®n amamangat…®z…®, a modogha dag…®abar na givezegha, na gakaghorima k…® kotiaba paza dar suisi, a? K…® arazir katam damight…®, ia na m…®kemeght…®, k…® anek…®righ uam a ikarvagham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® gumazamiziba kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBar puvat…®. N…® bizitam e gifarava, e gekuava arazir kuratam…®n e gamizir puvat…®. Egha gumazitam ataghiz…®, an akar is…®ngt…®zibar n…® m…®geima, n…® dar g…®n zuir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Kamagh…®n amiz…® Samuel ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko a m…®sevezir atrivim ian akar kam baregha g…®fa, egha fo ia nan dafarim…®n arazir kuratam…®n apizir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra. Ikiav…®ra Itir God fogha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 12:6 \xt Ua Me Ini 6:26\x*Egha Samuel ua kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, Ikiav…®ra Itir God fogha g…®fa. A fom…®ra Moses ko Aron am…®sefe, egha ian inazir afeziaba Isip…®n kantrin me inigha azenan kagh ize.  
\v 7 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia deragh kuariba arigh oragh, k…® kamagh…®n ia geghanasa, dughiar av…®riba Ikiav…®ra Itir God ingangarir aghuibagh amua ia ko, ian inazir afeziabar akurvaki.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 12:8 \xt Ua Me Ini 2:23\x*Ian ovavim Jekop uan adarazi ko me ghua Isip…®n iti, ez…® Isip…®n itir gumaziba arazir kurabar me gami, ez…® me uarir akurvaghasa Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®g…®ava araima, a me bagha Moses ko Aron amadaz…®, aning Isip…®n ian ovaviba inigha azenan iza kagh me at…®.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 12:9 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 3:12; 4:2; 13:1\x*Ez…® me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God, me a g…®n amada. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Hasor…®n nguibar ekiam…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim Sisera ataghiz…®, a iza me m…®sosi. Ez…® dughiar igharazim…®n, God Filistiaba ataghiz…® me iza me m…®sosi. Ez…® dughiar igharazim…®n, a Moapian atrivim ataghiz…®, a iza me m…®sogha me ab…®ni.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 12:10 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 10:10-15\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ian ovaviba pamtem…®n dia, kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®gei, ‚ÄòO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, e ak…®rim n…® gasaragha aser Balba ko aser amizim Astarten ziam fe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e arazir kuram gamigha g…®fa. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n en apanibar agharim…®n e iniasa, e ua n…®n azangs…®si, eght…® e n…® baghv…®ra ik…® n…®n ziamra fam.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 12:11 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 4:6; 7:1; 11:29; 1 Samuel 3:20\x*‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God men m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregha, Israelia bagha Gideon ko Bedan, Jepta ko k…® uab…® Samuel, a men akurvaghasa e amada. Guizbang…®ra, e gumazir dapaniba bar mogh…®ra ian apanibar agharibar ia ini, ez…® ia Israelia deraghav…®ra iti.\f + \fr 12:11 \ft Gideon…®n eghaghanim, a Gumazir Dapaniba sapta 6--8…®n iti. Ez…® Jeptan eghaghanim, a Gumazir Dapaniba sapta 11--12…®n iti. Ez…® Bedan…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba itir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumaziba ghaze, Bedan…®n ziar igharazim ti Barak, o Samson.\f* 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 12:12 \xt 1 Samuel 8:19\x*‚ÄúDughiar kaba bar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, a uab…®ra ian atrivim…®n ti. Egha ia garima, Amonian Atrivim Nahas iza ia ko m…®soghasa. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian atrivim…®n ikiasa ia ifongezir puvat…®, egha ia kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄòMark…®, N…® e bagh atrivitam am…®s…®vasa e ifonge.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúIa gan! Ian atrivir ia inabazimra kara, ia a bagha azaraz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a isa ia gan…®ngi!  
\v 14 Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiating an apengan ik…®. Egh ia an ziam f…®va an akaba baragh, ia uan atrivim ko ia bar, an Akar Gavgaviba zurara dar g…®n mang…®, eght…® God dabirabir aghuim ia dan…®ngam.  
\v 15 Eght…® ia oraghan kogh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgaviba batueght…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan gavgavim…®n, ia ko ian atrivim sara puv ia damigham.  
\v 16 Ia oragh. Ia tugh gavgavight…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bizir bar ekiatam damight…® ia an ganam.  
\v 17 Ia fo, kar wit…®n ov…®zir aniziba aghoramin dughiam, ez…® kar amozim…®n dughiam puvat…®. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®k…®mt…®, an ararim ko amozim damut…®, ararim dagaraght…®, amozim arigham. Eght…® ia ganigh fogh suam, ia arazir bar kuram…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n a gamigha, uari bagh atrivitam am…®s…®vasa an azara.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® dughiar kamra, Samuel Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®geima, an ararim ko amozim amadaz…®, ararim dagaraz…® amozim magh…®ram ar…®ki. Ez…® gumazamiziba bizir kam…®n ganigha Samuel ko Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiatingi. 
\p  
\v 19 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, gumazamiziba Samuel m…®gei, ‚ÄúE uari, gumazir aruam, e n…®n ingangarir gumazamiziba, e kamaghsua, n…® e bagh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God, a en apangkuvighs…® a m…®k…®m, eght…® e ovengan kogham. E fo, e arazir kurar av…®ribagh ami, e dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, e arazir kurar igharazir mam gamua, uari bagha atrivim am…®s…®vasa n…®n azara.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 \x - \xo 12:20 \xt God…®n Araziba 11:16\x*Ez…® Samuel kamagh…®n me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa atiatingan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra ia arazir kuram gamigha g…®fa. Egh ia bar ak…®rim ragh Ikiav…®ra Itir God gasan markiam. Ia guizbang…®ra an g…®n mang…®va, uan navir averiabar, bar mogh…®ra an ziam f…® an ingangarim damus…® gavgafigh.  
\v 21 Egh ia gavgaviba puvat…®zir asebar g…®n mangan mark…®. Da guizbang…®ra pura bizir k…®niba, eght…® os…®mt…®zibar dughiabar me ian akuragh ua ia inighan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham.  
\v 22 Bar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ifongiamra, a ia ginabaz…® ia an gumazamizibar otifi. A uan ziar ekiam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, egh ak…®rim ragh ia gasaraghan kogham.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 12:23 \xt 1 Atriviba 8:36; Aghuzir Akaba 4:11; Kolosi 1:9; 2 Timoti 1:3\x*Ia deraghv…®ra ik…®s…®, k…®rara God ko m…®k…®mamin ingangarim iti. K…® God ko m…®geir arazim ategham, mar k…® arazir kuram…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God gami. K…® arazir aghuiba ko vorogh…®ra zuir tuavibar ian sure damut…®, ia dar g…®n mang…®.  
\v 24 Ia bizir bar ekiar Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian akurvagha ia gamizibagh n…®ghnigh, egh zurara an atiating an apengan ik…®. Ia uan navir averiabar aven guizbang…®ra an g…®n mang…® an ziam f…®va, an ingangarim damus…® gavgafigh.  
\v 25 Egh ia arazir kurabar amuv…®ra ik…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia ko ian atrivim adugh ia avigh ia makunigham.‚Äù 
\c 13  
\s1 Israelia Filistiaba ko m…®sosi 
\p  
\v 1 Sol bar uan igiamra ikiava atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® azenir pumuning g…®vaz…®ma, bizir kam oto.\f + \fr 13:1 \ft Hibrun akam, namba 40 itir puvat…®, Sol…®n azenibar d…®bobonim ovenge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e deragha fozir puvat…®, d…®bobonir kam 40 guizbang…®ra o puvat…®. Gumazir av…®riba ghaze, Sol atrivim…®n itir azeniba, azenir pumuning gafiragha. Azenir kamning…®n, Samuel, Sol…®n danganim iniasa Devit am…®sefe. (N…® 1 Samuel 16.13…®n gan.) A Sol aremezir dughiam…®n m…®geir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 2 Dughiar kam…®n Sol ua bagha 3,000pla Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba am…®sevegha, igharaziba amadaz…®ma me ua nguibabar ghue. A m…®dorozir gumazir kabar tong…®n, 2,000pla iniz…®, me a ko Mikmas…®n nguibar ekiam…®n iti, a Betel…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar iti. Egha a uaghan m…®dorozir gumazir 1,000pla amadaz…®, me an otarim Jonatan ko, me Benjamin…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n aven, Gibean nguibar ekiam…®n iti.  
\v 3 Egha Jonatan uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me Geban nguibam…®n averpenibar itir Filistian m…®dorozir gumazibav sogha me ab…®ni. Ez…® Filistian igharaz darazi me arazir kam…®n akam baregha puv…®ra Israelian atari. Ez…® Sol bizir kam bagha gumaziba amadaz…®, me Israelian ik…®ziba bar dar ghua s…®ghabagh ivia, m…®dorozim…®n uab…®n akurvaghasa gumazibar dei.  
\v 4 Gumazir kaba kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúSol Filistian m…®dorozir gumazibar okoruar mam ab…®ra, kamagh…®n amiz…® Filistiaba dat…®r…®gh…®n bar Israelian apanim gami.‚Äù Ez…® gumaziba akar kam baregha iza Gilgal…®n nguibar ekiam…®n Sol ko uari akufa. 
\p  
\v 5 Dughiar kam…®n Filistian av…®riba iza Israelia m…®soghasa uari akufi. Me 3,000plan m…®soghamin karisba ko 6,000plan m…®dorozir gumazir hoziabar dapiamba iti. Men m…®dorozir gumaziba bar av…®raseme, mati ongarim…®n gigim. M…®dorozir gumazir kaba Mikmas…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghua me averpenibar ingarigha dar iti, Mikmas a Betaven…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n, aruem anadi nagh…®n iti.  
\v 6 Filistiaba ko Israelia uariv sosi. Ez…® Filistiaba bar pamtem…®n m…®sozima, Israelia uarir gari me m…®dorozim gafiraghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, Israelian marazi ghua nguazir toribar aven ghue, ez…® marazi benir epariabar aven monge, ez…® marazi m…®ghs…®am…®n dag…®ar toribar aven monge, ez…® marazi dag…®ar ekiabar tizibar monge, ez…® marazi mozir d…®pabar aven, dar ak…®ribar monge.  
\v 7-8 \x - \xo 13:7-8 \xt 1 Samuel 10:8\x*Ez…® marazi Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n otogha Gat ko Gileat…®n nguazim…®n vong…®n ghue. Sol Israelian g…®n m…®dorozim bagha ghuzir puvat…®. Samuel faragha 7plan dughiabar Gilgal…®n uab…®n m…®zuamasa a m…®keme. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Gilgal…®n ikia a m…®zuai. Ez…® gumazamizir a ko itiba me kamagh…®n oraki, Filistiaba m…®dorozim…®n Israelia ab…®ni, ez…® me bar atiatingi. Ez…® 7plan dughiaba g…®vaz…® Samuel izezir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamizir maba uari am…®k…®rvagha Sol atagh…®ragha tintinibar zui.  
\v 9 Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim ko God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofaba inigh na bagh iz…®.‚Äù Me da inigha izez…®, a da inigha ofa damuasa avim…®n bar ada tue.  
\v 10 Men ofan arazaraziba g…®vaz…®ma, Samuel izav oto. Ez…® Sol ofa gamir dakozim ategha azenan ghua, dughiam a gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄúAruer ar…®zir aghuim.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Samuel kamagh…®n Sol…®n azara, ‚ÄúN…® tizim gami?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® gumazamizibar garima me na atagh…®rasi. Ez…® k…® n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n n…® m…®zuaima, n…® izezir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® Filistiabar garima me Mikmas…®n uari bagha averpenibar ingari.  
\v 12 K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Filistiaba iz…® Gilgal…®n kagh e ko m…®sogham. Ez…® k…® navir aghuim Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngasa bizitam gamizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…® k…® ghaze, k…® ofan bar isi m…®gh…®ramibar amuam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Samuel kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúArazir n…® amizir kam bar onganigha derazir puvat…®. N…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God, n…® gan…®ngizir Akar Gavgaviba n…® dar g…®n zuir puvat…®. N…® ti an akabar g…®n ghuai, a n…® ko n…®n ovavir boriba ataghiz…®, ia zurara Israelia gativagha ikiai.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 13:14 \xt 1 Samuel 15:28; Onger Akaba 89:20; Aposel 13:22\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar ruarim…®n atrivim…®n ikian kogham. N…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akabar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gumazir aghuir mam ginaba, gumazir a bar ifongezim, a bar bizir God ifongezibar amuam. A God ifongezir arazibar g…®n zuir gumazim. Eght…® a God…®n gumazamizibar atrivim…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Samuel m…®kemegha g…®vagha Gilgal ategha nguibar igharazim…®n ghu. 
\p Ez…® Sol uaghan uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bativasa Gilgal ategha Gibean ghu. Ez…® Gilgal…®n itir gumazamiziba me bar an g…®n zui. Gibean nguibam, a Benjamin…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n iti. Me otivigha g…®vagha, Sol uan m…®dorozir gumazir a ko itiba medima, men d…®bobonim 600…®n borogh…®n ghu.\f + \fr 13:15 \ft Akar kam, ‚ÄúEz…® Sol uaghan uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bativasa Gilgal ategha Gibean ghu. Ez…® Gilgal…®n itir gumazamiziba me bar an g…®n zui. Gibean nguibam, a Benjamin…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n iti,‚Äù a Hibrun akam…®n itir puvat…®. Akar kam ti fom…®ra iti, egha g…®n ovenge. Akam ikiav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, gumazir maba Grik…®n akam…®n a g…®ra, ez…® akar kam Grik…®n akam…®n 1 Samuel…®n iti.\f* 
\v 16 Egha Sol uan otarim Jonatan ko, uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me ghua Benjamin…®n nguazim itir Geban nguibar ekiam…®n iti. Ez…® Filistiaba Mikmas…®n uan averpenibar iti.  
\v 17 Filistiabar m…®dorozir gumaziba 3plan okoruabar uarir tuiragha ghua Israelia ko m…®sosi. Okoruar mam not…®n amadaghan Sual…®n Distrigh…®n aven, Ofran nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.  
\v 18 Ez…® okoruar mam aruem uaghiri nagh…®n, Bethoron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu. Ez…® okoruar igharazim aruem anadir danganim…®n amadaghan ghu, kar gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim bagha zuir tuavim, n…® m…®ghs…®ar kam…®n zuir tuavim…®n mavanang beragh, munagh Afiar Atiaba Itir Danganir Zarim…®n ganam. 
\p  
\v 19 Dughiar kam…®n kantri Israel…®n gumazitam ain…®n bizitam…®n ingarizir puvat…®. Filistiaba faragha kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Hibruia m…®dorozir sababa ko afuzibar ingaran e aghua. N…®ghn…®zir kam bang…®n Filistiaba me ain…®n bizibar ingaran Israelian anogoroke.  
\v 20 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelia bar Filistiaba bagha zuima, me me bagha afaviba ko ain…®n nguazim ab…®ghamba ko sobiaba ko sabar ik…®z…®r…®ziba am…®ne.  
\v 21 Israelia zurara ingangarir kam bagha me givesi. Nguazim ab…®ghamin afaviba, ko sobiaba ko nguazim ab…®ghamin ain…®n igharagha gariba koma, bulmakaubar ag…®nt…®ghamin afuzir muziariba, bizir kaba bar, da am…®namin ivezim bar p…®n ko.  
\v 22 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, m…®dorozibar dughiabar, Sol ko Jonatan aningra m…®dorozir afuziba ko m…®dorozir sababa iti, ez…® Israelia bar puvat…®. 
\s1 Jonatan Filistiaba ab…®ni 
\p  
\v 23 Dughiar kam…®n Filistiaba m…®dorozir gumazir maba amadaz…®, me ghua Mikmas…®n borogh…®n m…®ghs…®ar ak…®rimning…®n t…®zim…®n zuir tuavim asigha iti. 
\c 14  
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar mam g…®vaz…®ma, Sol…®n otarim Jonatan kamagh…®n uan m…®dorozir gumazir igiar, an m…®dorozir afuziba ko oram…®n suizim…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGa vong…®n Filistiaba itir averpenibar mangam.‚Äù Egha Jonatan uan afeziam m…®kemezir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 2 Dughiar kam…®n, Sol uan purirpenim Mikron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n, temer pomigranet…®n povim…®n an ingarigha an iti, a Gibean borogh…®n iti. Ez…® 600plan m…®dorozir gumaziba a ko iti.  
\v 3 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazim Ahiya, a ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n korotiar azenan azuim atera, men tong…®n iti. Ahiya, a Ahitup…®n otarim, ez…® Ahitup, a Ikabot…®n aveghbuam, egha aning Finias…®n otarimning. Finias a Elin otarim, a fom…®ra Silon, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir gumazim. Ez…® Jonatan ghugha g…®fa, ez…® Sol…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, Jonatan ghu. 
\p  
\v 4 Jonatan uan namakam ko, Filistiaba averpenibar ingarizir tuavim…®n ghua, m…®ghs…®am…®n itir ak…®rir pumuning…®n t…®zim…®n itir tuavim…®n zui. Danganir kam, dag…®ar davarir dafar pumuning iti, mam vong…®n itima, mam vong…®n iti. Ez…® mam…®n ziam Boses, ez…® igharazim Sene.  
\v 5 Dag…®ar davarir mam not…®n amadaghan Mikmas…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itima, mam vong…®n saut…®n amadaghan Geban nguibar ekiam…®n iti. 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 14:6 \xt Gumazir Dapaniba 7:4; 7:7; 2 Eghaghaniba 14:11\x*Ez…® Jonatan dag…®ar davarir danganir kam…®n otogha kamagh…®n uan namakam m…®gei, ‚ÄúAria, ga vong…®n mang…®va Filistian Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®fozir puvat…®zir gumaziba, me uan m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorir puvat…®, ga me itir danganim…®n aven mangam. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ti gan akuraght…®, ga me ab…®ragham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®dorozim…®n apaniba ab…®nasava, gumazir av…®ribagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Ga uaningra deragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® an namakam kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera. N…® tizim damus…® n…® purama a damu. K…® navir vam…®ra n…® ko iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Jonatan kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar dera. Ga dat…®r…®gh…®n vong…®n mang…®va, uaning is…® Filistiabar akaght…®, me gan ganam.  
\v 9 Eght…® me uarir m…®zuams…® ga m…®k…®mt…®, ga danganir kamra tugh…®v ikiam. Ga me bagh mangan kogham.  
\v 10 Egh me suam, ‚ÄòGua iz…®,‚Äô eght…® ga me bagh mangam. Ga arazir kam…®n ganigh fogh suam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gan akuraght…®, ga me ab…®nam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, aning uaning isa Filistiabar akaz…®, me aning…®n gani. Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa munagh gan. Hibruian gumazir maba muna izi, me dag…®ar torir me aven modibar aven ikegha, azenim giregha izi.‚Äù  
\v 12 Ez…® Filistiabar m…®dorozir gumaziba, Jonatan uan namakam ko aning…®n d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúOi, gua kagh anang. E bizitam guan akakaghasa.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Jonatan m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha kamagh uan namakam m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan g…®n iz…® ga mangam. Ga dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me isa Israelia en agharim gat…®gha g…®fa.‚Äù  
\v 13 Egha Jonatan dag…®ar davarir kurar kam…®n ghua uan dafarimning…®n ua bagha suigha, suemning…®n iruem…®n ghuanadi mogh…®n an b…®ra ghuavanadi, ez…® an namakam kamagh…®ra an g…®n ghuavanabo. Ez…® Jonatan Filistian maba m…®sozima, me daighirima, an namakam an g…®n iza m…®dorozir sabam…®n me aghori me bar ariaghiri.  
\v 14 Ez…® faragha otozir m…®dorozir kam…®n, Jonatan uan namakam ko 20plan gumazibav soghez…® me ariaghire. M…®dorozir kam, danganir dozir mam…®n oto. 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Filistian m…®dorozir gumazir uan averpenibar itiba ko, m…®dorozir gumazir nguibabagh arua m…®soziba ko, Filistian igharaziba bar, m…®dorozir eghaghanir kam baregha n…®gha bar atiatingi. Ez…® m…®k…®mk…®zim nguazim…®n oto. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Filistiabar n…®ghn…®zibagh amiz…® da ikuviz…® me tintinibar are. 
\s1 Israelia Filistiaba ab…®ni 
\p  
\v 16 Dughiar kam…®n, m…®dorozir gumazir Sol Gibean nguibar ekiam…®n ganasa m…®seveziba, me ghua saghon mar garima, Filistiabar gumaziba onganiz…® mogh…®n tintinibar ivemaragha arui.  
\v 17 Me ghua Sol m…®kemez…®, Sol n…®ghn…®gha ghaze an m…®dorozir gumazitaba ti ghua Filistiabav soghama. Egha a kamagh…®n uan m…®dorozir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa m…®dorozir gumaziba d…®pon egh fogham te itir puvat…®.‚Äù Ez…® me kamagh…®n amigha fo, Jonatan ko an namakar an afuzim ko m…®dorozir biziba aterim itir puvat…®.  
\v 18 Dughiar kam…®n, God…®n Boksiam Gibean Israelia ko iti. Ez…® Sol, ofa gamir gumazim Ahiya m…®kemeght…®, a mang…® Boksiam inigh izam, eght…® me God…®n ifongiam bagh an azangs…®gham.  
\v 19 Sol ofa gamir gumazir kam…®n m…®g…®av…®ra itima, Filistiaba pamtem…®n dia, tintinibar uan averpenibar ikia ivemaragha arui, mati gumazir onganiba. Ez…® Sol me baregha ofa gamir gumazim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMark…®. N…® Boksiam ategh e m…®soghs…® mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Egha Sol uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko dia ivemara ghua Filistiabav sosi. Me garima, Filistiaba bar onganigha tintinibar uan akar gumazibara m…®sosi.  
\v 21 Hibrun marazi faragha ghua Filistian m…®dorozir gumazibar akurvagha men tong…®n iti, egha uaghan men averpenibar iti. Me dat…®r…®gh…®n Filistiaba ategha Sol ko Jonatan bagha izegha, uan akar gumaziba Israelian akuragha m…®sosi.  
\v 22 Israelian marazi, Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar muega iti, egha me kamagh…®n oraki, Filistiaba are. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma me iza Sol ko Jonatan…®n akuragha Filistiabar ag…®ra.  
\v 23 Me Filistiabar ag…®ragha ghua Betaven…®n nguibar ekiam gitagha s…®vagha ghu. Dughiar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian akuraz…®, me m…®dorozim…®n Filistiaba ab…®ni. 
\s1 Bizir m…®dorozim…®n g…®n otiviziba 
\p  
\v 24 Dughiar kam…®n Sol akar gavgavim Israelia m…®keme. A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra uan apanibar os…®mt…®ziba ikaragh m…®zazim me gasam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n daghetam aman kogh mang…® guarat…®zim…®n tugh. Gumazitam daghetam ameght…® God a gas…®ghas…®gham.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelian gumazitam daghetam amezir puvat…®gha, m…®tiriam bang…®n am…®ragha gavgaviba puvat…®.  
\v 25 Egha me ghua ruarir mam…®n otogha garima, hanin m…®konir dafar mam nguazim…®n itima, hanin bar av…®rim an aven iti.  
\v 26 Me fo, Sol akar gavgavim me gan…®ngiz…® me atiatigha, hanibar gara tam amezir puvat…®.  
\v 27 Ez…® Jonatan kamagh…®n oraghizir puvat…®, an afeziam daghebar aman uan m…®dorozir gumazibar anogoroke. Egha a suigha aruir aghorim…®n ruaghatevim…®n hani garugha aneme. An amegha g…®vagha zuam…®ra ua gavgavim ini.  
\v 28 Ez…® gumazir mam kamagh…®n Jonatan m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n afeziam dughiar kam…®n daghebar aman en anogoroke, kamagh…®n amiz…® e m…®tiriam bang…®n am…®ra. A pamtem…®n kamagh…®n e m…®gei, gumazitam daghetam ameght…® God a gas…®ghas…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® Jonatan kamagh…®n gumazir kam m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan afeziam…®n akar kam, os…®mt…®zim isa en nguazir kam…®n itir gumazibagh an…®ngi. Ia nan gan. K…® hanin bar muziarim amegha ua gavgavim ini.  
\v 30 E uan apaniba da inizir dagher kaba ameghai, egha gavgavim inighai. E Filistian mabav soke, egha e ti daghetaba amegha gavgavigha, Filistian bar av…®rir tabar m…®sueghai.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 31 Dughiar kam…®n, Israelia Mikmas…®n nguibar ekiam…®n apanibav sogha ghua, Aijalon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, m…®tiriam bar puv…®ra men azima me gavgaviba puvat…®.  
\v 32 Aruem iraghugha g…®vaz…®ma me ivemara ghua, sipsipba ko bulmakaun me uan apaniba da iniziba ini. Egha me zuam…®ra pura nguazim…®n dav sueghava dar tuziba inigha ghuziba sara purama da api. 
\p  
\v 33 \x - \xo 14:33 \xt Ofa Gami 7:26-27; 17:10-14; 19:26; God…®n Araziba 12:16; 12:23; 15:23\x*Ez…® gumazir maba ghua kamagh…®n Sol m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh. M…®dorozir gumaziba ghuziba itir as…®ziba ame, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram gami.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Sol akar kam baregha d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAmei, ia gumazir bar kuraba. Ia bar ak…®rim God gasara.‚Äù 
\p A kamagh…®n gumazir akam inigha izezibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa dag…®ar ekiatam poghpogh na bagh iz…®.\f + \fr 14:33 \ft God as…®zir ghuziba itiba aman Israelian anogoroke. N…® Jenesis 9:4…®n gan.\f* 
\v 34 Egh ia tintinibar mang…® m…®dorozir gumazibav m…®kemeght…®, me bulmakauba ko sipsipba inigh iz…®. Egh me dag…®ar kam…®n dav suegh, da tuegh kagh dar amam. Egh me ghuziba sara dar ameghan koght…®, arazir kam…®n me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram gamizir puvat…®.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, d…®magarir kamnagh…®ra, m…®dorozir gumaziba bulmakauba inigha iza danganir kamra dav soke.  
\v 35 Ez…® Sol dag…®ar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingari, kar ofa gamir dakozir, Sol bar faraghav…®ra ingarizim. 
\p  
\v 36 Ez…® Sol g…®n uan gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAria, e d…®mangan mag…®r…®va, Filistiabar ag…®ragh me m…®sogh mang…®t…® am…®nim tiragham. Egh e bar me m…®sueght…® me ar…®ghireght…®, e men biziba bar ada iniam.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, e mamagh…®ra damuam.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® ofa gamir gumazim ghaze, ‚ÄúE ti faragh…®v…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azaragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 37 Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n God…®n azara, ‚ÄúE mang…® Filistiabav sogham o markiam? N…® en amamangat…®gh…®va, en akuraght…® e me ab…®nigham o?‚Äù Dughiar kam…®n God a ikarazir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 38 Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n Israelian gumazir dapanibav gei, ‚ÄúIa iz…®. E uarira uarir buri fofogham, tina arazir kuram gamiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God en akam barazir puvat…®.  
\v 39 Ikiav…®ra Itir God zurara ikiava, Israelia en akurvasi, ez…® an ziam…®n k…® akar gavgavim gamua ghaze, gumazir manam arazir kurar kam gami an ovengam. Nan otarim Jonatan uaghan arazir kurar kam damigh, a uaghan ovengam.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir kabar tong…®n gumazitam, an akam ikarazir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 40 Ez…® Sol bar Israelia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa bar mogh…®ra vong…®n munagh tuifigh, eght…® k…® uan otarim Jonatan ko ga vong…®n kagh tugham.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, n…® manmagh…®n damuasa ifonge, n…® damu. E n…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n mang…® mamagh…®ra damuam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 41 \x - \xo 14:41 \xt D…®boboniba 27:21; 1 Samuel 28:6\x*Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azara, a Israelian God, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® tizim bagha nan akaba ikarvazir puvat…®? Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® Israelian God. K…® uab…®, o nan otarim Jonatan arazir kurar kam damight…®, n…® ofa gamir gumazim damight…®, a God…®n ifongiam g…®foghs…®, mang…® dag…®ar kamning…®n tong…®n, dag…®ar faragha itim inigh. Egh gumazir igharazitam arazir kurar kam damight…®, n…® ofa gamir gumazim damight…®, a mang…® dag…®ar kamning…®n tong…®n dag…®ar namba 2 inigh.‚Äù Ez…® God a baregha ofa gamir gumazim gamiz…®, a dag…®ar Sol ko Jonatan…®n ababanim…®n itim ini, ez…® gumazamizir igharaziba puvat…®.\f + \fr 14:41 \ft Vez…®n kam…®n akar otevir maba, da Hibrun akam…®n itir puvat…®. Akar kaba ti fom…®ra iti, egha g…®n ovenge. Ez…® akar kaba ikiav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, gumazir maba Grik…®n dagh ira, ez…® akar kaba Grik…®n akam…®n 1 Samuel…®n iti.\f* 
\p  
\v 42 Ez…® Sol dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIngangarir kamra, ia uam a damigh e ganika, tinara arazir kuram gami, Jonatan o k…® uab…®.‚Äù Ez…® me kamagh…®n amiz…®ma dag…®am Jonatan ginaba. 
\p  
\v 43 Ez…® Sol Jonatan…®n azara, ‚ÄúN…® tizim gami?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Jonatan ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® hanin bar muziarim asadivir aghorir k…® suirazim…®n ruaghatevim…®n a inigha aneme. Ez…® mark…®, k…® aremegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 44 Ez…® Sol a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, n…® aremegham. N…® aremeghan koght…®, k…® God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram damigham, eght…® God na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 45 Ez…® gumazamiziba kamagh…®n Sol m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh. Jonatan Israelia en akuraz…®, e m…®dorozir ekiar kam gafira. A ti aremegham, a? Bar puvat…®gham. E Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…® bizir kuratam…®n a damuan mark…®. God an akuraz…®, a bizir kam gami.‚Äù Kamagh amiz…®, gumazamiziba ua Jonatan iniz…®ma, Sol a m…®soghez…® an aremezir puvat…®.  
\v 46 Bizir kam…®n g…®n, Sol ua Filistiabar ag…®razir puvat…®. Ez…® Filistiaba uamategha uan kantrin ghue. 
\s1 Atrivim Sol ko, an adarasi 
\p  
\v 47 Sol Israelian atrivim…®n otogha g…®vagha, uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me Israelian apanir tintinim…®n danganibar itibav sosi. Me Moapia ko Amonia, Idomia ko Filistiaba ko Soban kantrin atrivibav sosi. Me m…®dorozibar zurara uan apaniba m…®zazim me gasa me ab…®ri.  
\v 48 Egha Sol uan m…®dorozir gumazibar naviba fema, me pamtem…®n m…®sogha uaghan Amalekia ab…®ni. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, men apaniba ua iza Israelia m…®sozir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 49 Ez…® Sol…®n otaribar kara, Jonatan, Isvi ko Malkisua. Ez…® an guivimning, avenemebam…®n ziam, Merap, ez…® an afumim Mikal.  
\v 50 Ez…® Sol…®n amuim…®n ziam, Ahinoam a Ahimas…®n guivim. Ez…® Sol…®n m…®dorozir gumazir dapanim, an ziam Apner, a Ner…®n otarim. Ner a Sol…®n afeziar dozim.  
\v 51 Ez…® Sol…®n afeziam Kis. Ez…® Kis ko Ner, aning Abiel…®n otarimning. 
\p  
\v 52 Sol atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, an m…®dorozir gumaziba pamtem…®n Filistiabav sosi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a zurara gumazir gavgaviba buri. A gari, gumazir manam m…®dorozibar atiatir puvat…®, an a inight…®ma, an an m…®dorozir gumazim…®n otogham. 
\c 15  
\s1 Sol Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam batoke 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 15:1 \xt 1 Samuel 10:1\x*Dughiar mam, Samuel kamagh…®n Sol m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiar k…® Israelian atrivim…®n ikiasa n…® am…®sevezim, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamiziba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® na amadaz…®, k…® kamagh…®n ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam baragh.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 15:2 \xt Ua Me Ini 17:8-14; God…®n Araziba 25:17-19\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòIan inazir afeziaba Isip ategha azenan izir dughiam…®n, Amalekia pazav…®ra me gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam.  
\v 3 Kamagh amiz…®, n…® uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigh mang…® Amalekia ko m…®sogh men biziba bar dagh as…®ghas…®kigh. Egh gumazamiziba ko boriba, bulmakauba, sipsipba, kamelba ko donkiba bar dav sueght…®, da bar ar…®ghiregh. Ia tav ateght…® a ikian bar mark…®.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Sol kamagh…®n oregha, uan m…®dorozir gumazibar diaz…®, me iza Telem…®n nguibam…®n uari akufa. Ez…® men d…®bobonim kamagh…®n zui, Judan m…®dorozir gumaziba me 10,000, ez…® Israelia 200,000.  
\v 5 Ez…® Sol g…®n uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha, Amalekian nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n ghue. Kar danganir d…®pam fom…®ra ivemarim, a dat…®r…®gh…®n dakez…® me an mongegha iti.  
\v 6 Ez…® Kinia Amalekian borogh…®n iti. Ez…® Sol akar gavgavim me bagha anemaga ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Amalekia ategh mang…® danganir igharazitam…®n ik…®. Puvat…®ght…®, e mang…® me m…®soght…® ia me sara ar…®ghiregham. En inazir afeziaba fom…®ra Isip ategha azenan izir dughiam…®n, ian inazir afeziaba deraghav…®ra Israelia e gami. K…® ian inazir afeziabagh n…®ghnigha ia bagha akam amadi. Kamagh…®n, ia ar…®ghiram k…® aghua.‚Äù Ez…® Kinian gumazamiziba kamagh…®n oregha Amalekia ategha ghue.  
\v 7 Ez…® Sol pamtem m…®sogha Amalekia ab…®ni, a Havilan nguazim…®n ikegha ghua Sur…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghua, Isip…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n tu.  
\v 8 Egha Sol Amalekian Atrivim Agak…®n suira. Ez…® Israelia Amalekian igharaz darazi bar me m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire.  
\v 9 Me Agak…®n m…®soghez…® an aremezir puvat…®, egha me uaghan bulmakauba ko sipsip…®n aghuibav soghezir puvat…®. Me bulmakauba ko sipsip…®n kuraba ko as…®zir igharazir k…®nibav soghez…® da ariaghire. 
\s1 Sol uam atrivim…®n ikian God aghua 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n Samuel m…®gei,  
\v 11 \x - \xo 15:11 \xt Jenesis 6:6-7; 1 Atriviba 9:6-7\x*‚ÄúN…® oragh, Sol nan akaba batuegha ak…®rim na gasara. Ez…® nan navim kamagh…®n mong oseme, k…® Sol atrivim…®n ikiasa a ginaba. Bizir kam bang…®n nan navim derazir puvat…®.‚Äù Ez…® Samuel akar kam baregha navim osemegha atari, egha d…®magarir kam…®n Samuel Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®g…®a an diav…®ra itima am…®nim tira. 
\p  
\v 12 Bar m…®zaraghara Samuel d…®kavigha Sol bagha zui. Ez…® me a m…®g…®a ghaze, Sol Karmel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghugha, m…®dorozim gafiragha ziar ekiam ini. Bizir kam bagha, a dag…®ar ababanim asara. An anesaragha g…®vagha Gilgal…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.  
\v 13 Samuel ghua Sol batogha dughiam Sol gan…®ga ghaze, aruer aghuim, ‚ÄúSamuel, Ikiav…®ra Itir God deraghv…®ra n…® damu. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgavim…®n g…®n ghugha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Samuel a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGuis…®? Ez…® k…® tizim bagha bulmakauba ko sipsipbar arareba barasi?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúNan m…®dorozir gumaziba, Amalekia dam ada ini. Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofa damuasa, bulmakauba ko sipsip…®n aghuiba ini, a en God. Egha bulmakauba ko sipsip…®n kuraba me bar dav soke.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Samuel kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® asugh n…®m…®ra ik…®. K…® bizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God d…®mangan na m…®kemezim…®n gun n…® m…®k…®mam.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Sol ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, n…® na m…®k…®m.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Samuel kamagh…®n Sol m…®gei, ‚ÄúFom…®ra n…® ghaze n…® pura bizim, n…® Israelian anababar gumazir dapanim. Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® n…® ginabaz…®, n…® atrivim…®n oto.  
