\v 27 \x - \xo 15:27-28 \xt 1 Samuel 28:17; 1 Atriviba 11:30-31\x*Egha Samuel ragha mangasava amima, Sol pamtem…®n an korotiar av…®zim…®n suiraz…® a b…®ki.  
