\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. N…® bulmakaun amebar igiar otezir puvat…®zitam inigh, ua Betlehem…®n mang…®va gumazamizir nguibar ekiam…®n itibar m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofa damuasa izi.‚Äô  
\v 3 Egh n…® Jesin azaraght…®ma a uaghan ofan kam bagh iz…®t…®, k…® bizir n…® damuamim…®n gun n…® m…®k…®mam. Egh gumazir k…® atrivim…®n otivasa m…®sevezim, k…® n…®n akakaght…®, n…® borem is…® an dapanim gingegham.‚Äù 
