\v 7 \x - \xo 16:7 \xt Onger Akaba 147:10-11; Aisaia 55:8\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, an aghuir ruarim ko an ganganiba deraght…®, k…® a ginabagham. Puvat…®. Gumazir kam, atrivim…®n otivan k…® aghua. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gumaziba biziba tuis…®si mogh…®n, biziba tuis…®zir puvat…®. Gumaziba uan damazibar inivaf…®zibar gari. Ez…® k…® gumazibar n…®ghn…®ziba ko men ifongiabar gara me tuis…®si.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Jesi uan otarir namba 2…®n dia, an ziam Abinadap, egha a inigha Samuel bagha ize. Ez…® Samuel ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a ginabazir puvat…®.‚Äù 
