\v 12 Ez…® Jesi gumazir mam amadaz…®, a ghua an otarir kam inigha izi. Jesin otarir kam, a uan mugamra ikia an guam bar deraz…® an damazimning dafoz…®, an m…®karzim…®n ganganiba bar dera. 
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Samuel m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA mara, gumazir mamra, an atrivim…®n otivam. N…® atriviba am…®s…®va me gazuir borem is…®, a gingegh.‚Äù 
