\v 16 N…® ifueght…® e mang…® n…® bagh, gitan m…®n garir d…®b…®arir strinba itibav sozir gumazitam batogham. Eght…® God, n…® bagh duar kuram amangamin dughiabar, gumazir kam n…® bagh d…®b…®arim m…®soght…®, an ararer aghuim n…® damut…®, n…®n n…®ghn…®zim ua deragham.‚Äù 
