\v 20 Ez…® Jesi oregha Sol bagha Devit amadi. Jesi ak…®rar pumuning…®n bretba aghuigha, donkin mam…®n ak…®rim gikegha, da isa Devit gan…®ngi. A uaghan memen inim…®n ingarizir m…®sevir wain ruizim sara a gan…®ngi. Egha memen igiar mam sara a gan…®ngi, a kamagh…®n Devit m…®g…®a ghaze, bizir kaba, n…® bizir aghuibar m…®n Atrivim Sol dan…®ngigh.  
\v 21 Ez…® Devit ghua Sol batogha an ingangarir gumazim…®n oto. Ez…® Sol bar Devit gifonge, egha uan m…®dorozir biziba ateramin ingangarim isa Devit gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n Jesi bagha akam amada, ‚ÄúK…® Devit gifonge. K…® kamaghsua, n…® aneteght…® a nan ingangarir gumazim…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Devit Sol ko iti. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, duar kuram Sol bagha anemadir dughiabar, Devit d…®b…®arim m…®sozima an ararer aghuim gami. Ez…® Sol gitan m…®n garir d…®b…®arir ararer kam barazima, duar kurar kam Sol atagh…®razima, an n…®ghn…®zim ua araragha izima, a ua dera. 
\c 17  
\s1 Goliat pamtem…®n Israelian dei 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Filistiabar m…®dorozir gumaziba g…®n iza Efesdamim…®n uari akuvagha uari ak…®ri. Me nguibar kam…®n uan averpeniba ingari, danganir kam Aseka ko Sokon nguibar ekiamning…®n t…®zim…®n iti. Egha me Sokon Israelia ko m…®soghasa.  
\v 2 Ez…® Sol Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua, Elan danganir zarim…®n ikia Filistiaba ko m…®soghasa uari ak…®ri.  
\v 3 Ez…® Filistiaba vong…®n m…®ghs…®ar mam…®n itima, Israelia vong…®n m…®ghs…®ar igharazim…®n iti, ez…® danganir zarim aning ab…®ki. 
\p  
\v 4 Dughiar kam…®n, m…®dorozir gumazir bar dafar gavgavir mam, a Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazim, an ziam Goliat. A Filistiabar averpeniba ategha iza azenara tuz…®, Israelia an gari. An ruarim 3 mitan borogh…®ra ghu.  
\v 5 Egha a bras…®n ingarizir dapanir asuam ko m…®dorozir korotiaba aghui, ez…® dar os…®mt…®zim 50 kilogrem…®n tu.  
\v 6 A bras…®n otevir mamning…®n uan suemning noke, Egha bras…®n ingarizir afuzim gisaghpu.  
\v 7 An afuzir m…®siam m…®temegha ekevegha, mati ter otevir mam. Ez…® afuzir m…®zem me ain…®n an ingariz…®, an os…®mt…®zim 7 kilogrem…®n tu. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir mam oram…®n suiragha an faragha zui. 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Goliat tugha pamtem…®n Israelian d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha m…®dorozim damuasa m…®kefi? Ia m…®soghasa, a? Ia pura Sol…®n ingangarir gumazir k…®niba, ez…® k…® Filistiabar m…®dorozir gumazim. Aria, ia gumazitam am…®seveght…®, a iz…® na m…®sogh.  
\v 9 A gavgavigh na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeght…®, e pura ian ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar ikiam. Eght…® k…® a m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, ia en ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Egha Goliat ua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa oragh. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba ian ingarav ak…® ia basamasa. Ia gumazitam am…®seveght…® a iz…® na ko m…®sogham.‚Äù  
\v 11 Ez…® Sol uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko akar kam baregha, me bar atiatigha n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh ami. 
\s1 Devit a Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba bagha zui 
\p  
\v 12 Devit…®n ik…®zim…®n eghaghanim kamak…®n, Devit a Jesin otarim. Jesi a Efratan nguibar ekiam…®n gumazir mam. A Betlehem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n iti. Betlehem, a Judan anabam…®n nguazim…®n iti. Ez…® Jesi otarir 8pla iti, ez…® Sol atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Jesi ghurigha g…®fa.  
\v 13-14 Ez…® Jesin otarir ivariam Eliap, an g…®rara irim Abinadap, ez…® otarir m…®kezim Sama, me Sol…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar akuragh apanibav soghasa ghue. Ez…® Devit a Jesin otarir dozir abuananam.  
\v 15 Dughiar mabar Devit ghua Sol…®n ingangaribagha ami. Egha dughiar maba, a Sol atagh…®ragha ghua Betlehem…®n uan afeziam…®n sipsipbar gari. 
\p  
\v 16 Dughiar kam…®n, Goliat 40plan m…®zaraziba ko guarat…®zibar iza azenara tuiva, uab…® ko m…®soghasa Israelian d…®a ghaze, ia gumazitam amadaght…® a iz…® na ko m…®sogh. 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® dughiar mam…®n Jesi kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® bret…®n 10plan kaba ko 10 kilogrem…®n wit…®n me avim…®n tueziba inigh, zuam…®ra uan aveghbuaba bagh averpenir me itibar mang…®.  
\v 18 N…® uaghan 10plan sis…®n dagher kaba inigh mang…® m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanim dan…®ngigh. Egh uan aveghbuabar azaragh, me derav…®ra iti, o puvat…®. Egh me da bizitam inigh iz…® nan akaght…® k…® fogham, me derav…®ra iti.  
\v 19 N…® mang…® gant…®, Atrivim Sol ko n…®n aveghbuaba ko m…®dorozir gumazir igharaziba, me Elan danganir zarim…®n ikia Filistiaba ko m…®sosi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® am…®mzaraghan, Devit bar m…®zaraghara d…®kavigha sipsipbar ganasa gumazir igharazim m…®keme. Egha a dagheba inigha, men averpeniba iti nagh…®n zui, mati Jesi a m…®kemez…® mok…®n. A ghua otivima, Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba m…®dorozim bagha ghua, pamten dia zui.  
\v 21 Ez…® Filistiabar m…®dorozir gumaziba vong…®n tuivighav iti, ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba vong…®n tuivigha, m…®dorozim bagha uari ak…®ri.  
\v 22 Ez…® Devit dagheba isa d…®penim…®n itir bizibar garir gumazim ganigha, ivegha ghua m…®dorozir gumazibar tong…®n uan aveghbuabav g…®a ghaze, ia dera?  
\v 23 A me ko m…®g…®av…®ra itima, Filistian m…®dorozir gumazir bar gavgavim Goliat, a Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazim, a Filistian m…®dorozir gumaziba ategha iza azenara tugha, Israelian d…®a m…®geir akar kamra uam a gami, ez…® Devit a barasi.  
\v 24 Ez…® Israelia Goliat…®n garava bar atiatigha are. 
\p  
\v 25 Egha Israelia kamagh…®n uariv gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazir munam…®n gan…®va an d…®mdiam baragh. A m…®dorozim bagha e gaghora en ingaravati. Ez…® en atrivim kamagh…®n m…®gei, gumazitam Filistian kam m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, a dag…®ar av…®riba ko bizir av…®riba a dan…®ngam, egh a uaghan uan guivim ateght…®, gumazir kam an ikiam. Eght…® atrivim uaghan gumazir kam…®n adarazi da dag…®aba inian kogham, egh atrivim uaghan uan ingangariba bagh men d…®man kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® Devit deragha akar kam baraghizir puvat…®gha kamagh…®n an borogh…®n itir gumazibar azai, ‚ÄúGumazir manatam Filistian gumazir kam m…®sueght…®, an aremeght…®, Israelian aghums…®zir kam g…®vagham, eght…® atrivim manmagh…®n a damuam? K…® kamagh…®n gari, Filistian kam, a gumazir God g…®fozir puvat…®zim, egha uan m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim atuzir puvat…®. A uab…® fava d…®bovir akabar God…®n Zurara Itim…®n m…®dorozir gumazibav gei.‚Äù  
\v 27 Ez…® gumaziba a geghari, atrivim kamagh…®n m…®gei, gumazir manam Goliat m…®sueght…®, a bizir kabar a damuam. 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Devit…®n avebam Eliap orazima, Devit gumaziba ko m…®gei. Ez…® an navim ikuviz…®ma a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha kagh ize? Tinara n…®n sipsip…®n muziariba gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n dar gara dagh eghufi? K…® fo, n…® ifari, n…® orazi puvat…®gha puv…®ra ifaghatir gumazim. N…® pura daru m…®dorozim…®n ganasa ize, biziba puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n uan avebam m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. K…® bizitam g…®fofoghasa gumazibar azangs…®si. K…® kamagh…®n amima, a ti deraz, o puvat…®?‚Äù  
\v 30 Egha a ragh…®r…®gha ua gumazir igharazibar azai, gumazir Filistian gumazim m…®sueght…® an aremeghamim, atrivim manmagh…®n a damuam? Ez…® me ua bizir Sol faragha m…®kemezibar a m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® gumazir maba Devit…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baregha ghua Sol m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Devit…®n diaz…®ma an a bagha ghu. 
\p  
\v 32 Ez…® Devit ghua otogha kamagh…®n Sol m…®gei, ‚ÄúO atrivim, n…® oragh. E Israelia, e Filistian kam…®n atiating…®va osemeghan kogham. K…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, k…® uab…® mang…® a ko m…®sogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 33 Ez…® Sol ghaze, ‚ÄúBar puvat…®. N…® otarir bar igiam. N…® manmagh…®n a ko m…®sogham? N…® otarir agh…®rir k…®nim. Goliat uan igiamra m…®dorozir gumazim…®n ikia iza dat…®r…®k…®n.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 34 Ez…® Devit Sol…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, k…® uan afeziam…®n sipsipbar gari. Ez…® dughiar mabar laionba ko beaba iza sipsip…®n nguziba isa zui.  
\v 35 Ez…® k…® laionba ko bean kabar ag…®nt…®gha dav sogha dar akatoribar uam sipsip…®n nguziba, me dama da isi. Eght…® laion o bea ragh na m…®soghs…® iz…®t…®ma, k…® an tuer ar…®zibar suiragh an gurim ap…®right…® an aremegham.  
\v 36 O atrivim, Filistian gumazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®fozir puvat…®zir kam, a gumazir uan m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim atuz…® puvat…®zim, a d…®bovir akaba God…®n m…®dorozir gumazibav gei. Ez…® k…® laionba ko beabav soghez…® mogh…®n, arazir kamra, k…® a damuam.  
\v 37 Ikiav…®ra Itir God nan akuraz…®, laionba ko beaba na gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, a uaghan nan akuraght…®, Filistian kam na m…®sueghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Sol a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, n…® mang…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® ko ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 38 Egha Sol dapanir asuar bras…®n ingarizim…®n an dapanim garugha, korotiar bras…®n ingarizim an m…®karzim avasa a gan…®ngi. Kar Sol…®n m…®dorozir korotiaba.  
\v 39 Ez…® Devit m…®dorozir sabam inigha bras…®n m…®dorozir korotiam arugha, uab…® baraghav arui. Ez…® puvat…®, a fom…®ra bizir kamagh gari taba aghuizir puvat…®. Kamagh amiz…®, a Sol m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® m…®dorozir korotiar kabar aghuigh mang…® m…®soghan kogham. K…® bizir kaba azuir puvat…®.‚Äù Kamagh amiz…®, a ua da sue.  
\v 40 Egha a uan asadivir aghorim inigha daghurir d…®par mam…®n eghuravim…®n ghuava 5plan dag…®ar guar doziba inigha, uan m…®tarir dozim garu. Egha uan katapel…®n suiragha Goliat bagha zui. 
\s1 Devit m…®dorozim…®n Goliat ab…®ra 
\p  
\v 41 Ez…® Filistian gumazim Goliat, a garima, Devit a bagha arua izi. Ez…® Goliat Devit bagha izi. Ez…® gumazir Goliat…®n oram…®n suizim an faragha zui.  
\v 42 Ez…® Goliat Devit…®n garima, a bar otarir igiam, ez…® an guam…®n ganganiba bar dera. Ez…® Goliat ghaze, a ti m…®dorozim damuamin fofoziba puvat…®, a pura borir k…®nim.  
\v 43 Kamagh…®n amiz…® a Devit d…®pova kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagh asadivir aghorir mam…®n suiragha izi? N…® ghaze, k…® ti afiam, egha na m…®soghasa, a?‚Äù Egha a Devit gas…®ghas…®ghasa uan asebar dei. 
\p  
\v 44 Egha a kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® iz…®t…®, k…® n…® m…®suegh n…®n kuam is…® kuarazir isaba ko as…®zir atiabar anight…®, me n…® amam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 45 \x - \xo 17:45 \xt 2 Samuel 22:33-35; Onger Akaba 124:8; Hibru 11:33-34\x*Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® m…®dorozir sabam ko afuziba inigha na m…®soghasa. Ez…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim…®n ziam…®n n…®n m…®soghasa izi, a Israelia en m…®dorozir gumaziba gativazir God. A God…®n kamra, n…® an akaba barazir puvat…®gha d…®bovir akabar a m…®gei.  
\v 46 N…® oragh. Dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar kamra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® is…® nan dafarim dat…®gham. Eght…® k…® n…® m…®suegh n…®n dapanim atugham. Egh e ian m…®dorozir gumazibav suegh, men namnaba is…® kuarazir isaba ko as…®zir atiabar an…®ngam. K…® kamagh…®n damight…®, kantribar gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n fogham, Israelian God, a guizbang…®ra God.  
\v 47 Eght…® gumazamizir kagh itiba bar kamagh…®n ganigh suam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan gumazamiziba uan gavgavimra me isi. A gumazir afuziba, ko m…®dorozir sababar suiziba, a dagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® m…®dorozir kam damuam, egh bar ia is…® en dafarim dar…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 48 Devit m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, Goliat ua bar s…®vagha Devit…®n borogh…®ra izi. Ez…® Devit zuam…®ra ivegha ghua Goliat m…®soghasa zui.  
\v 49 Devit dafarim uan m…®tarir dozim garugha, dag…®ar mam inigha uan katapel gat…®gha a ighengegha Goliat gase. Ez…® dag…®am an guam m…®t…®gha a vuigha an dapanim…®n aven ghuz…®, a guam mogh…®n ira uaghira nguazim…®n fuaghav iti.  
\v 50 \x - \xo 17:50 \xt 2 Samuel 21:19\x*Kamagh…®ra, Devit katapel ko dag…®am…®n m…®dorozim…®n Goliat m…®soghez…® an areme. A m…®dorozir sababa puvat…®.  
\v 51 Goliat nguazim gir…®ghav itima, Devit ivegha ghua Goliat…®n borogh…®n tugha, an m…®dorozir sabam am…®k…®r…®gha an f…®rim atuz…®, an areme. Ez…® Filistiaba garima men faragha zuir m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavim aremegha g…®vaz…®, me bar mogh…®ra tintinibar are. 
\p  
\v 52 Ez…® Israelia ko Judan gumaziba dagarvagha, men ag…®nt…®gha me m…®sozima me ariaghiri. Ez…® Filistiabar kuaba tintinibar Saraim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tuavim girav ikia ghua, Get…®n nguibar ekiam ko Ekron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazim…®n tiar akabar tu.  
\v 53 Ez…® Israelia men ag…®ntigha g…®vagha, uamategha ghua Filistiabar averpenibar men bizir me tegha areziba ini.  
\v 54 Ez…® Devit Goliat…®n kuam…®n namnam…®n itir m…®dorozir biziba bar da inigha ghua uan averpenim gat…®. Egha Goliat…®n dapanim inigha ghua Jerusalem…®n itir gumazamizibar akakaghasa, eght…® me fogh suam, a m…®dorozim…®n Goliat ab…®ragha g…®fa. 
\s1 Devit ghua Sol…®n gani 
\p  
\v 55 Sol garima, Devit ghua Goliat ko m…®sozima, ez…® a kamagh…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar faragha zuir gumazir dapanim Apner…®n azai, ‚ÄúOtarir igiar kam, a tinan otarim?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Apner a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, k…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, k…® fozir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 56 Kamagh amiz…®, Sol ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® tintinibar gumazir igharazibar azangs…®gh, egh iz…® na m…®kemegh.‚Äù  
\v 57 Ez…® Devit Goliat m…®soghez…® an aremez…® dughiam…®n g…®n, a uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghuz…®, Apner a inigha Sol bagha ghu. Ez…® Devit Goliat…®n dapanim…®n suiraghav…®ra ikia Apner ko ghua Sol bato. 
\p  
\v 58 Ez…® Sol an azara, ‚ÄúOtarir igiam, n…® tinan otarim?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Devit a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, k…® Jesin otarim, a n…®n ingangarir gumazim, a Betlehem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazir mam.‚Äù 
\c 18  
\p  
\v 1 Sol Devit ko m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, Sol…®n otarim Jonatan, a uan navir averiam sara Devit bar a gifonge, egha uab…® gifongez…® mogh…®n bar a gifonge. Egha aning bar namakar aghuimning…®n oto.  
\v 2 Dughiar kam…®n, Sol Devit iniz…® an a ko iti, egha anetaghiz…®ma a uamategha uan nguibam…®n ghuzir puvat…®.  
\v 3 Jonatan bar Devit gifonge, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, an akar gavgavir mam…®n Devit ko anek…®ri. Ez…® Devit uaghan Jonatan ko akam ak…®ri.  
\v 4 Ez…® Jonatan uan korotiar aghuir ruarim ko m…®dorozir korotiaba sara sue. Egha bizir kaba ko an m…®dorozir sabam ko an barir pim ko an benir uab…® am…®gh…®rim sara da isa Devit gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Devit Sol ko itima, Sol Devit m…®geima, a m…®dorozir gumaziba isa ghua apanibav sosi, egha m…®sozir dughiabar, Devit zurara m…®dorozibar uan apaniba ab…®ri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Sol m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanir mam…®n ikiasa a ginaba. Ez…® gumazamiziba ko m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir igharaziba, kamagh…®n Devit…®n gara, bar a gifonge. 
\s1 Sol Devit baseme 
\p  
\v 6 Devit Goliat m…®soghez…® an aremegha g…®vaz…®, m…®dorozir gumaziba bar uamategha nguibabar izi. Me tuavim…®n izima, Israelian nguibar ekiabar amiziba uan nguibar ekiaba ategha azenan iza tuavim…®n atrivim Sol bato. Me bar akongezir ighiabagh amua gitan m…®n garir d…®b…®arim ko tambarinbav sosi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 18:7 \xt 1 Samuel 21:11; 29:5\x*Egha me kamagh…®n ighiam bange: 
\b  
\q1 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòSol 1,000plan apanibav sosi. 
\q1 Ez…® Devit 10,000plan apanibav sosi.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 8 Sol ighiar kam baregha, bar an aghuagha puv atari. Egha navim ikuvigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe ti ghaze, Devit apanir bar av…®ribav soke, ez…® k…® gumazir vabara m…®soke, ez…® a bar na gafira. Me ti kamaghsua, a ti g…®n nan danganim inigh atrivim…®n ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 9 Dughiar kam…®n, Sol bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha Devit…®n gara a basei. 
\p  
\v 10 Am…®mzaraghan Sol uan d…®penim…®n iti, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, duar kurar mam a bagha anemada. Bar zuam…®ra duar kurar kam Sol…®n n…®ghn…®zim ab…®raz…®ma, Sol pura diava arai, mati gumazir onganim. Dughiar kam…®n Devit uan gitan m…®n garir d…®b…®arim…®n gikararai, mati a dughiabar zurara ami mogh…®n ami. Ez…® Sol uan afuzim…®n suiragha,  
\v 11 kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n afuzim…®n Devit giniv a is…® b…®rim gikeght…® ana aremegham.‚Äù Egha an afuzim Devit m…®k…®niz…®, Devit an afuzim gita. Sol dughiar pumuning…®n arazir kam gamiz…®, Devit dughiar pumuning…®n an afuzim gita. 
\p  
\v 12 Sol fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Devit ko iti, egha ak…®rim ragha Sol gasara. Kamagh amiz…®, Sol Devit…®n atiatingi.  
\v 13 Egha a Devit ataghiz…®, an atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n itir puvat…®. Sol g…®n Devit amadaz…®, a 1,000plan m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim…®n iti. Ez…® Devit m…®dorozir gumazir kaba inigha ghua apanibav sosi.  
\v 14 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Devit ko ikia an akurvazima, bizir bar av…®rir an amiba deraghav…®ram otifi.  
\v 15 Ez…® Sol Devit…®n garima an ingangariba bar deragha otivima, a bar puv…®ra Devit…®n atiati.  
\v 16 Devit m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapanir bar aghuim, kamagh amiz…®ma, Israelia ko Judabar gumazamiziba bar a gifongegha a baghav…®ra iti. 
\s1 Devit Sol…®n guivim…®n iti 
\p  
\v 17 Egha Sol kamagh…®n ifonge, ‚ÄúDevit aremeght…® deragham. K…® ti uab…® a m…®sueghan kogham. A ti uab…® Filistiaba ko m…®soght…®, Filistiaba a m…®sueght…® an aremegham.‚Äù 
\p Kamagh amiz…®, Sol kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh, k…® Merap n…® dan…®ngasa, a nan guivir ivariam, eght…® gua uaning…®n ikiam. Ez…® k…® ua kamagh…®n n…® m…®k…®masa, bizir n…® na bagh damuamim, n…® nan m…®dorozir gumazim…®n m…®n ik…® pamtem…®n ingar atiatingan mark…®. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ifueght…® e uan apanibav soghamin dughiam…®n, n…® mang…® me m…®sogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Devit Sol…®n akar kam baregha kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúMark…®, k…® an ikian kogham, k…® gumazir k…®nim. Egha uaghan nan adarazi ziaba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…® k…® n…®n guivim…®n ikian kogham.‚Äù  
\v 19 Ez…® Sol gavgavigha ghaze, Devit Merap…®n ikiam, egha aning uaning…®n ikiasa dughiam am…®sefe. Dughiar aning uaning…®n ikiamim otoz…®, a d…®kavigha Merap isa gumazir igharazim gan…®ngi, an ziam Adriel, a Meholan nguibar ekiam…®n gumazir mam. 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® g…®n Sol…®n guivir igharazim, an ziam Mikal, a Devit bagha bar ifonge. Ez…® Sol bizir kam baregha bar akonge.  
\v 21 Egha a kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúBar dera. K…® Mikal Devit dan…®ngam. Egh k…® Devit amadaght…®, a mang…® Filistiabav sogham, eght…® Filistiaba a m…®sueght…®ma an aremegham.‚Äù 
\p Kamagh amiz…®, Sol ua Devit…®n diagha a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® kamagh…®n ifonge n…® nan guivim…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 22 Egha Sol uan ingangarir gumazir maba amaga ghaze, ia mang…® Devit…®n ganigh, dughiar Devit uab…®ra ikiamim, ia an apezeper suam, ‚ÄúAtrivim Sol bar n…® gifonge, ez…® e an ingangarir gumaziba uaghan n…® gifonge. N…® oragh. Dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® an guivim…®n ikiamin dughiar aghuim.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Egha me ghua m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n Devit m…®gei. Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa ti ghaze, k…® dag…®aba itir gumazim, egha ziam itir gumazim, egh atrivim…®n guivim…®n ikiam, a? Bar puvat…®gham. K…® biziba puvat…®zir gumazir k…®nim. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® an ikeghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ingangarir gumaziba uamategha ghua, Devit m…®kemezir akabar gun Sol geghari.  
\v 25 Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, a Devit amadaght…®, a mang…® Filistiaba ko m…®soght…®ma, me a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uan ingangarir gumazibav kemeght…®, me uamategh mang…® Devit m…®k…®mam. A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® kamaghsua, Devit bizir bar vam…®ra nan guivim gives…® na dan…®ngam. K…® kamaghsua, Devit nan apaniba ikarvagh…®va 100plan Filistian m…®dorozir gumazibav sueght…® me ar…®ghiregh. Egh a 100plan gumazir kabar m…®karzir mogomebar inibar ghoregh, da inigh na bagh iz…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® Sol…®n ingangarir gumaziba ghua Sol…®n akabar gun Devit m…®gei. Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, arazir kam, a Sol…®n guivim givezamin arazir aghuim, egha a Sol…®n amerem…®n otivasa bar akonge. Egha Sol m…®karzir mogomer inir kaba inigh izasa dughiam ginaba. Ez…® dughiar kam t…®ghar otivam,  
\v 27 ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua Filistiabar m…®dorozir gumazir 200pla m…®suegha, men m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghoregha, da inigha atrivim bagha izegha da medi. Devit Sol…®n guivim…®n ikiasava arazir kabagh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Sol uan guivim Mikal isa Devit gan…®ngiz…® aning uaning…®n iti. 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Sol dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n deragha fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Devit ko iti, ez…® Mikal uaghan bar Devit gifonge.  
\v 29 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, Sol Devit…®n atiatiav…®ra ikia egha bar an aghua. Egha Sol zurara an apanim…®n iti. 
\p  
\v 30 Dughiar av…®ribar, Filistiabar m…®dorozir gumazir dapaniba uan m…®dorozir gumazibar akua, Israelia m…®soghasa izi, ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko pamtem…®n me m…®sogha me ab…®ri. Sol…®n m…®dorozir gumazir dapanir igharaziba, me Devit pamtem…®n m…®sozi mogh…®n m…®sozir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba ziar ekiam Devit gan…®di. 
\c 19  
\s1 Jonatan Devit…®n akura 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Sol Devit m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa uan otarim Jonatan ko uan ingangarir gumaziba bar me m…®keme. Ez…® Jonatan bar Devit gifonge.  
\v 2 Egha a ghua Devit m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan afeziam n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghasa m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® gurumzaraghan bar deraghv…®ra uab…® geghuv, egh mang…® azenibar modogh.  
\v 3 Eght…® k…® afeziam ko, ga mang…® danganir n…® modozim…®n borogh…®n tugh…®v ik…®t…®, k…® n…® bagh afeziam…®n m…®k…®m…®va an n…®ghn…®zim g…®fogham. A manmagh…®n n…® damus…® damut…®, k…® an gun n…® m…®k…®mam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Egha am…®mzaraghan, Jonatan ko Sol ghua uaning m…®g…®a, Jonatan Devit…®n ziam fa kamagh…®n Sol m…®gei, ‚ÄúAfeziam k…® bizitam n…® m…®k…®masa. A kamak…®n. N…® arazir kuratam uan ingangarir gumazim Devit damuan mark…®. An arazir kuratam…®n n…® gamizir puvat…®. Bizir av…®rir an amiba da n…®n akurvasi.  
\v 5 A Goliat m…®soghez…® an aremez…® dughiam, a kamagh…®n uab…® g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, an ovengam o an angam…®ra ikiam. Devit…®n agharim…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelia en akurvaghav…®ra ikia, en apaniba, a bar me ab…®ni. Ez…® n…® uab…® bizir kam…®n ganigha bar akonge. A bizitam gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® tizim bagh puram a m…®sueght…® an aremegham? N…® kamagh…®n damigh os…®mt…®zir ekiam inigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Sol Jonatan…®n akaba baregha, akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim gamua ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n, k…® Devit m…®sueght…® an aremeghan kogham.‚Äù  
\v 7 Ez…® Sol m…®kemegha g…®vagha ghuz…®, Jonatan Devit…®n diaz…®ma a izima, an eghaghanir an afeziam a m…®kemezibar gun a geghari. A g…®n Devit inigha Sol bagha ghuz…®, Devit fom…®ra atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n ingariz…® mogh…®ra ua ingari. 
\s1 Sol Devit m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa 
\p  
