\v 2 Ez…® Jonatan kamagh…®n Devit ikara, ‚ÄúPuvat…®, n…® aremeghan kogham. Nan afeziam, bizir a damuamiba, a bar dar gun na m…®gei, bizir muziariba ko bizir ekiaba. Egh a bizir katam nan modoghan kogham. Ez…® k…® fo, a n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghan kogham.‚Äù 
