\v 5 \x - \xo 20:5 \xt D…®boboniba 28:11\x*Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGurumzaraghan iak…®nir igiam…®n dughiar ekiam…®n, k…® mang…® atrivim ko damam. N…® uab…® n…®ghn…®gh, n…® na amadaght…®, k…® mang…® obarir azenim…®n modogh ik…®, mang…® am…®mzaraghan guarat…®zim…®n tugham.  
\v 6 Eght…® n…®n afeziam apir dakozim…®n na bagh gan…®va n…®n azangs…®gh suam, a managh iti, eght…® n…® kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòAzeniba vaghvagha dar dughiar kam…®n, Devit…®n adarazi me uari akuva Betlehem…®n ofabagh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a mangasa nan azaraz…®, k…® an amamangat…®z…®, a uan nguibam…®n ghu.‚Äô  
