\v 2 Ez…® Devit ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim ingangarir mam na gan…®ngiz…® k…® izi. A ghaze, k…® damuamin ingangarir kam, k…® an gun gumazir igharazitam m…®k…®man kogham. K…® uan m…®dorozir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ia danganir igharazitam…®n na batogh.  
