\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 21:6 \xt Ofa Gami 24:5-9\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ofa gamir gumazim bretba isava a gan…®ngi. Bret…®n me isa God gan…®ngizim anar…®ra iti. Dagher igharaziba ua puvat…®. Me dughiar kam…®n God…®n damazim…®n bret…®n igiaba isa, ghuribar danganim gar…®gha, dakozim gat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ofa gamir gumazim, bret…®n ghuriba isa Devit gan…®ngi.  
\v 7 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Atrivim Sol…®n ingangarir gumazir mam, a Idomian gumazim, an ziam Doek. A God…®n Purirpenim…®n ikia God…®n ofa damuamin dughiam m…®zuai. A garima Ahimelek bret…®n kaba isa Devit gan…®ngi. Doek a Sol…®n bulmakaubar garir gumazibar gumazir dapanim.  
\v 8 Ez…® Devit bretba inigha kamagh Ahimelek m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® afuzitam o m…®dorozir sabatam iti? N…® tam ik…®va na dan…®ngigh. Atrivim ingangarim bagha nan av…®si, k…® m…®dorozir sabatam o bizir igharazitam inizir puvat…®. K…® pura ize.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 21:9 \xt 1 Samuel 17:51\x*Ez…® Ahimelek a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® m…®dorozir sabar vam…®ra iti. Kar Goliat…®n m…®dorozir sabam, n…® Elan danganir zarim…®n a m…®soghez…® an areme. Me a isa nir mam…®n a noegha ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim azenim…®n azuir korotiar otevim…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n anet…®. N…® ifuegh m…®dorozir sabar kam iniam.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Devit ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® a is…® na dan…®ngigh! M…®dorozir sabar kam, a bar dera. Tam uam a gafirazir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 21:10 \xt 1 Samuel 21:13; Onger Akaba 34:1\x*Egha Devit Sol…®n atiatigha dughiar kamra nguibar ekiar kam ategha arav ghu. A ghua Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim Akis bato.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 21:11 \xt 1 Samuel 18:7; 29:5\x*Atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazibar dapaniba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam Devit, a uan kantrin atrivim. Amiziba a bagha kamagh ighiam bange: 
\b  
\q1 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòSol 1,000plan apanibav sosi. 
\q1 Ez…® Devit 10,000plan apanibav sosi.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 21:12 \xt Onger Akaba 56:1\x*Ez…® Devit m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Get…®n nguibam…®n garir Atrivim Akis ti a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. Egha an atiati.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 21:13 \xt Onger Akaba 34:1\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Devit atrivim ko an ingangarir gumazibar dapanibar damazim…®n, odava gumazir onganim gava. Me a ikiasava amima a bar gumazir onganim…®n m…®rarama oto. A pura tintinibar nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n, biziba osira diava arava, pupuviba an akatorim…®n otiva an ghuamas…®zim…®n izaghiri. 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Atrivim Akis an gara kamagh uan ingangarir gumazir dapanibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa kagh gan, gumazir kam bar ongani! Ia tizimsua a inigha na bagha izi?  
\v 15 Ia ti ghaze, nan kantrin gumazir onganiba puvat…®, a? Bar av…®riba iti, kamagh amiz…® ia tizim bagha gumazir onganir kam inigha izima, an arazir onganiba nan damazim…®n dagh amuav…®ra iti? A nan d…®penim…®n ikian kogham.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, Atrivim Akis Devit ataghiz…®ma, a ghu. 
\c 22  
\s1 Sol ofa gamir gumazibav soghez…®, me ariaghire 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 22:1 \xt Onger Akaba 57:1; 142:1\x*Egha Devit Get…®n nguibar ekiam ategha ara ghua, Adulam…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n dag…®ar torir mam…®n iti. Ez…® an aveghbuaba ko an afeziam…®n ik…®zim kamagh…®n oraki, a danganir kam…®n iti. Ez…® me ghua a ko iti.  
\v 2 Dughiar kam…®n, gumazir os…®mt…®zir igharagha garir av…®riba itiba ko, gumazir igharaz darazir biziba inigha da ikarazir puvat…®ziba ko, gumazir adariba gumazir igharazibar itiba, me bar mogh…®ra Devit bagha ghuegha a ko uari akuvagha itima, a men gumazir dapanim…®n iti. Gumazir a ko itibar d…®bobonim, 400…®n borogh…®n ghu. 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Devit uan amebam ko afeziam inigha danganir kam ategha, Moap…®n kantrin, Mispan nguibar ekiam…®n ghu. Egha a kamagh…®n Moapian atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® kamaghsua, n…® nan amebam ko afeziam ateght…®, aning n…® ko ik…®t…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ifongiam g…®fogham, a na bagh a bizir tizim damuam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Moapian atrivim, Devit ifongez…® mogh…®n, a Devit…®n amebam ko afeziam inigha izima aning Moap…®n atrivim ko itima, Devit uab…® dag…®ar torim…®n modogha iti. 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam, an ziam Gat, a iza kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ua danganir kam…®n ikian mark…®. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra d…®kavigh Judan anabam…®n nguazim…®n mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® Devit danganir kam ategha, Judan nguazim…®n ghua an ruarir ekiar me kamagh…®n d…®borim Heret…®n ghugha an iti. 
\p  
\v 6 Dughiar mam, Sol Gibean m…®ghs…®ar dozim…®n ikia, temer mam…®n apengan aperaghav ikia, uan afuzim…®n suiraghav iti. Ez…® an ingangarir gumazibar dapaniba an okarigha iti. Ez…® gumazir maba Devit itir danganim…®n gun a m…®gei.  
\v 7 Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa Benjamin…®n anabam…®n gumaziba, ia derav…®ram oragh. Ia ti ghaze, gumazir kam Devit, a dagher azeniba ko wain…®n azeniba is…® ia dan…®ngam, a? Egh a ia damut…® ia 1,000pla ko 100plan m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanibar otivam, a? Bar puvat…®gham.  
\v 8 K…® fo, ia bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®gha na gas…®ghas…®ghasa akam m…®soke. Ian tav bar kamagh…®n na m…®kemezir puvat…®, nan otarim, Jesin otarir kam…®n akurvaghasa a ko akar gavgavim ak…®ri. Ia na g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®gha, kamagh…®n na m…®kemezir puvat…®, nan otarim a nan ingangarir gumazir kam gamiz…®ma, a nan apanim…®n oto. Egha a dat…®r…®gh…®n na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeghasa tuaviba buri.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 22:9-10 \xt Onger Akaba 52:1\x*Dughiar kam…®n Idomian gumazim Doek, a Sol…®n ingangarir gumaziba ko tuivighav iti. Egha a kamagh…®n Sol m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Nop…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikia garima, Devit ofa gamir gumazim Ahimelek bagha ghu, a Ahitup…®n otarim.  
\v 10 Ez…® Ahimelek, Devit mangamin tuavim bagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei. Egha a dagher maba ko Filistian gumazim Goliat…®n m…®dorozir sabam sara inigha Devit gan…®ngi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Sol akar kam baregha gumazir maba amadaz…®ma, me ghua Nop…®n ofa gamir gumazim Ahimelek ko an ik…®zim…®n itir ofa gamir gumaziba bar me inigha ize.  
\v 12 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir kaba bar otivigha g…®vaz…®ma, Sol kamagh…®n Ahimelek m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Ahitup…®n otarim, n…® oragh. K…® akar mam n…®n iti.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Ahimelek ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, n…® akar manam iti?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúBizir tizim bagha n…® Jesin otarim ko, gua na gas…®ghas…®ghasa akam ak…®ri? N…® dagher maba ko m…®dorozir sabar mam sara a gan…®ga, aka taba a dan…®ngasa God…®n azangs…®si. A dat…®r…®gh…®n nan apanim gavagha, na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeghasa tuaviba buri.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Ahimelek kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBar puvat…®. Devit a n…®n ingangarir gumazibar faragha zuir gumazir bar aghuim, egha a deraghav…®ra n…®n g…®rara zui. Ingangarir gumazitam a gafirazir puvat…®. A uaghan n…®n amerem, a n…®n borogh…®n ikia n…® geghuvir m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir mam. N…®n d…®penim…®n aven itir adarasi, me bar a gifuegha ziar ekiam a gan…®di.\f + \fr 22:14 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 15 Dughiar kamra k…® ti akatam a dan…®ngasa God…®n azangs…®si, o? Bar puvat…®. K…® dughiar av…®ribar a bagha God ko m…®gei. K…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, k…® uan adarazi ko, n…® akam e gasan mark…®. E n…® gas…®ghas…®ghasa akam ak…®rizir puvat…®. Bizir n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n m…®geir kam, k…® bar a g…®fozir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. Ahimelek, k…® n…® bareghan kogham. N…® uan adarazi ko bar ovengam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Egha Sol uan m…®dorozir gumazir an borogh…®n tuivighav itibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAria. Ia ragh…®r…®gh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir gumaziba m…®sueght…®, me ar…®ghiregh. Me Devit ko ingara fo, a nan aragharui, ez…® me bar na m…®geir puvat…®.‚Äù Sol kamagh…®n m…®geima, m…®dorozir gumaziba me m…®soghan aghua. Me fo, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir gumaziba. 
\p  
\v 18 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Sol Doek m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® me m…®sueght…® me ar…®ghiregh.‚Äù Ez…® Doek ragh…®r…®gha ghua ofa gamir gumaziba bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Dughiar kamra a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir gumazir 85pla m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Gumazir kaba, me ofa gamir gumazir korotiar otevir azenan azuiba.  
\v 19 Ez…® Sol uan m…®dorozir gumaziba amadaz…®ma me Nop…®n ghue, kar ofa gamir gumaziba itir nguibar ekiam. Egha me Nop…®n gumazamiziba bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Me gumaziba, ko amiziba, boriba ko borir agheghevir oteba apiba, bulmakauba, donkiba, ko sipsipba sara bar me kuavareme. 
\p  
\v 20 Egha me Ahimelek…®n otarim Abiatar, a Ahitup…®n igiavotarim, me a m…®soghezir puvat…®. A men ara ghua Devit ko iti.  
\v 21 Ez…® Abiatar kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúSol Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir gumaziba bar me m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúNoka! Dughiar k…® n…®n afeziam ko ikezim, Doek uaghan iti. Ez…® k…® fo, a guizbang…®ra nan gun Sol m…®k…®mam. K…® fo, na bang…®n, n…®n afeziam uan adarazi ko ariaghire. Kar nan os…®mt…®zimra!  
\v 23 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® ik…®va atiatingan mark…®. Ga fo, gumazir na m…®soghasava amim, a uaghan n…® m…®soghasa. N…® na ko ik…® deraghv…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\c 23  
\s1 Devit Keilan nguibam…®n akura 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® gumazir maba iza kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúFilistiaba Keilan nguibam…®n itir gumazamizibav sogha, men wit…®n ov…®zibar iniba kua dar dagheba isir danganim…®n ghua, men wit…®n dagheba okeme.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 2 Ez…® Devit akar kam baregha kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azai, ‚ÄúK…® mang…® Filistiabav sogham o markiam?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera. N…® mang…® Filistiabav suegh Keilabar akuraght…®, me deragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Devit ko itir gumaziba a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® oragh. E dat…®r…®gh…®n Judan anabam…®n nguazim…®n itima, bizir av…®riba e gamima, e atiatingi. E manmagh…®n Keilan nguibam…®n mang…® Filistiabav sogham? E mangan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Me kamagh…®n m…®kemez…®ma, Devit uam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azai. Ez…® a ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ian akuraght…®ma, ia m…®dorozim…®n Filistiaba ab…®nigham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, ia d…®kavigh Keilan nguibam…®n mang…® Filistiabav sogh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Devit uan gumaziba ko, Keilan ghua pamtem Filistiabav soghez…®, men av…®riba ariaghire. A bar me ab…®ragha, men bulmakauba ini. Kamagh…®ra, Devit Keilan nguibam…®n gumazamizibar akuraz…®, me derav…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 6 Ahimelek…®n otarim Abiatar, faragha Atrivim Sol…®n ara iza Devit ko itir dughiam…®n, a ofa gamir gumazibar korotiar otevir azenan azuim inigha ize.\f + \fr 23:6 \ft Korotiar kam, a ofa gamir gumazibar korotiar otevir azenan azuim, a dag…®ar pumuning iti. Aning God…®n ifongiam g…®foghamin ingangarim iti.\f* Me Keilan nguibam…®n zuir dughiam…®n, Abiatar korotiar kam uaghan a inigha me ko zui.\f + \fr 23:6 \ft Fom…®ra itir gumazir maba, ak…®nafarir kam Grik…®n akam…®n a giragha an osiri. Egha me ghaze, Hibrun akam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n iti. Ez…® e garima, ak…®nafarir Hibrun akam…®n dat…®r…®gh…®n itir kam, akar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, Abiatar faragha Keilan nguibam…®n Devit bato.\f* 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® gumazir maba Sol m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDevit ghua Keilan nguibar ekiam…®n iti.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Sol ghaze, ‚ÄúBar dera, God dat…®r…®gh…®n a isa nan agharim dar…®gham. Devit a nguibar ekiar tiar akar gavgavim ko d…®vazir gavgavim itim…®n aven ize. A uab…® uab…® isa kalabuziam gat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® an suighamin ingangarim osemezir puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 8 Kamagh…®n amiz…® Sol uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bar men diaz…®, me Devit uan adarazi ko me konasa Keilan zui. 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n oraki, Sol a gas…®ghas…®ghasa izi. Ez…® a kamagh…®n ofa gamir gumazim Abiatar m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ofa gamir gumazibar korotiar otevir azenan azuir kam, a inigh iz…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® an a inigha izez…®, Devit kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®gei, ‚ÄúO, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® Israelia en God, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, k…® kamagh…®n oraki, Sol fo, k…® Keilan kagh iti. Kamagh amiz…®, a na bang…®n kagh iz…® nguibar kam gas…®ghas…®ghasa.  
\v 11 K…® foghasa, nguibar kam…®n gumazamiziba na is…® Sol dan…®ngam, o puvat…®gham? Sol izamin akam a guizbang…®ra o puvat…®? O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelia en God, nan ifongiam kamak…®n, n…® nan azangs…®zim ikaragh.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúSol a izam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Devit ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azara, ‚ÄúKeilan gumazamiziba, me k…® uan adarazi ko e is…® Sol dan…®ngam, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù Ez…® a ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, me n…® m…®gei mogh…®ra mamagh…®ra damuam.‚Äù  
\v 13 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n oregha zuam…®ra uan gumaziba ini, men d…®bobonim 600…®n m…®n tu. Me bar d…®kavigha Keila ategha ghue. Me bar mogh…®ra uari inigha tintinibar danganibagh arui. Ez…® Sol orazima Devit Keila ategha arav ghuz…®ma, Sol ua Keilan mangan n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. 
\s1 Devit a m…®ghs…®aba itir danganibar modi 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Devit ghua Sif…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n, m…®ghs…®aba itir danganir mongamin aghuibar modi. Danganir kam, kar danganir dak…®rt…®zir gumaziba puvat…®zim. Sol zurara Devit buriav…®ra iti, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Sol gamima, a Devit bativir puvat…®.  
\v 15 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n fo, Sol iz…® a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, a ghua Sif…®n borogh…®n Hores…®n nguibam…®n iti.  
\v 16 Ez…® Sol…®n otarim Jonatan Devit…®n ganasa ghua, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ikiasa akar aghuibar a m…®gei.  
\v 17 Egha Jonatan kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan afeziam n…® buri n…® batogh, n…® gas…®ghasighan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® atiatingan mark…®. N…® g…®n Israelian atrivim…®n ikiam, eght…® k…® n…®n g…®rara ikiam. Nan afeziam, a uaghan bizir kam g…®fo.‚Äù  
\v 18 \x - \xo 23:18 \xt 1 Samuel 18:3\x*Egha aning Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n, roroamning…®n ikiasa akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir mam gami. Egha Jonatan uamategha uan nguibam…®n ghuz…®ma, Devit Hores…®n ikiav…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 23:19 \xt Onger Akaba 54:1\x*Ez…® Sif…®n gumazir maba ghua Gibean nguibar ekiam…®n Sol m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO atrivim, n…® oragh. Devit en bighan Hakilan m…®ghs…®am…®n modogha iti, a saut…®n amadaghan Jesimon…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n iti. Me Hores…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n, m…®ghs…®abar m…®soghamin danganir aghuibar iti.  
\v 20 O atrivim, e fo, n…® gumazir kam…®n suighasa bar ifonge, n…® iz…®va a inigh. E uari a is…® n…®n agharim dar…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® Sol kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa nan akurvaghamin arazir aghuim gami. Bizir kam bang…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God deraghv…®ra ia damu.  
\v 22 K…® fo, gumaziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, Devit bar d…®k…®rm…®ki, an e gifaragham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uamategh mang…® a itir danganim bagh deraghv…®ra ganigh, egh uaghan gumazir an ganizibar ziaba inigh.  
\v 23 Ia bar deraghv…®ra a modozir danganibagh fogh, egh zuam…®ra iz…® na m…®kemeght…®, k…® ia ko mangam. A danganir kamra ik…®t…®, k…® mang…® deraghv…®ra a batogham. K…® Judabar dakoziba bar dar tong…®n a buriva an apigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Sol m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, Sifia anetegha uan nguibam…®n ghue. Egha me kamagh…®n fo Devit uan gumazamiziba ko me Maon…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n iti. A saut…®n amadaghan, Jesimon…®n Jordan…®n danganir zarim…®n iti.  
\v 25 Sol oregha g…®vagha, uan gumaziba ko me danganir kam…®n ghua Devit buri. Ez…® gumazir maba iza Devit m…®keme. Ez…® a ghua danganir kurar dag…®ar av…®riba itim…®n, Maon…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganir vuem…®n iti. Sol oraght…®, Devit danganir manam…®n mang…®t…®, a uaghan danganir kam…®n mangam.  
\v 26 Sol uan gumaziba ko m…®ghs…®ar ak…®rir vuem…®n mang…®t…®, Devit uan adarazi ko me sol…®n ar…®va, m…®ghs…®ar ak…®rir vuem…®n mangam. Egha Sol uan adarazi ko ghua bar Devit uan adarazi ko me ikiarugha bar men suighasava ami.  
\v 27 Ez…® gumazir mam iza kamagh…®n Sol m…®gei, ‚ÄúFilistiaba en nguazim…®n izegha e m…®sosi. Ez…® n…® zuam…®ra uamategh iz…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Sol akar kam baregha uan gumaziba ko me Devit ategha, uamategha ghua Filistiaba ko m…®sosi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me danganir kam d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúM…®dorozibagh Itaghv…®razir Dag…®am.‚Äù  
