\v 1 Sol Filistiabar ag…®ragha g…®vagha, ua iza Devit buri. Ez…® gumazir maba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® munagh gan, Devit muna Engedin borogh…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n iti.‚Äù  
\v 2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Sol Israelian 3,000plan m…®dorozir gumaziba am…®sevez…®ma, me Devit ko an gumaziba buri. Me danganir kurar kamagh…®n d…®borim, Memen Atiaba Itir Danganir Kuram, me an me buri.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 24:3 \xt Onger Akaba 57:1; 142:1\x*Me ghua sipsipba itir d…®vazir mabar borogh…®n, m…®ghs…®ar torir mam…®n iti. Ez…® Sol daviasa torir kam…®n aven ghu. Ez…® Devit uan gumaziba ko, faragha torir kam…®n, bar an aven ghugha an modogha iti. 
