\v 4 Devit…®n gumaziba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAria. Dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n dughiar aghuim, Ikiav…®ra Itir God an gun n…® m…®kemegha g…®fa, a n…®n apanim n…®n agharim dar…®gham. Eght…® n…® arazir manam…®n a damus…® a damu.‚Äù Ez…® Devit n…®m…®ra an amuda ghua, Sol…®n borogh…®n ghugha, an korotiar ruarim…®n v…®n an av…®zir mam atu, ez…® Sol fozir puvat…®.  
\v 5 Devit anetugha g…®vagha n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, arazir kam derazir puvat…®. 
