\v 6 \x - \xo 24:6 \xt 1 Samuel 26:11\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, Devit uamategha ghua uan gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God uab…® gumazir kam ginabagha a isa nan gumazir ekiam…®n anet…®. Kamagh amiz…®, k…® arazir kuratam…®n a damuan kogham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® nan anogoroke, k…® bizir kam damuan kogham.‚Äù  
\v 7 Egha Devit uan gumazibar atarigha men amamangat…®zir puvat…®, ez…® me ghua Sol…®n m…®soghezir puvat…®. Ez…® Sol avigha g…®vagha, torir kam…®n azenim gir…®gha tuavim gir…®gha ghu. 
