\v 8 Ez…® Devit an g…®rara torir kam…®n azenim gir…®gha an g…®rara ghua an diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim Sol, nan gumazir ekiam.‚Äù Ez…® Sol d…®md…®ar kam baregha ragh…®r…®z…®, Devit uan tevimning ap…®righa, guam nguazim tuagha ziar ekiam a gan…®di. 
\p  
\v 9 Egha a kamagh…®n Sol m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha gumazir kabar akaba baragha ghaze, k…® n…® gas…®ghas…®ghasa?  
\v 10 N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n uan damazimning kagh gan, n…® dag…®ar torim…®n itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® isa nan dafarim gat…®. Ez…® nan adarazi ghaze, n…® a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Ez…® k…® n…®n apangkuvigha ghaze, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God inabazir atrivim, k…® a m…®sueghan kogham.  
\v 11 Nan afeziam, n…® kagh k…® suirazir nir av…®zir kam…®n gan. K…® n…®n korotiar ruarim…®n av…®zim atugha n…® m…®soghan aghua. Kamagh amiz…®, n…® deragh na g…®fogh, k…® n…®n apanim puvat…®, egha paza n…® g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Egha os…®mt…®zitam n…®n itir puvat…®. Ez…® n…® na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeghasa na buriav…®ra iti.  
\v 12 Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…®, gan araziba tuis…®gh egh fogh suam, gan tinara arazir kuram gami. A, n…® amizir arazir kurar kam bagh n…® ikarvagh, ivezir kuram n…® dan…®ngam. Eght…® k…® uab…® arazitam n…® damighan kogham.  
\v 13 N…® aghuzir akar fom…®ra itir kam g…®fo, ‚ÄòGumazir kurabara, arazir kurabagh ami.‚Äô Ez…® k…® gumazir kuram puvat…®, k…® arazir kuratam…®n n…® gamizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 24:14 \xt 1 Samuel 26:20\x*O Israelian atrivim, n…® nan ag…®nt…®ghasa izi, o? Ez…® k…® tina? K…® mati afiam aremegha g…®fa. K…® mati pir mam.  
\v 15 Kamagh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® ga tuis…®gh m…®k…®m suam, gan tinara os…®mt…®zim gami. A uan kot…®n aven nan akuragh na bagh akam ak…®right…®, n…® na gas…®ghas…®ghan kogham.‚Äù 
