\v 16 Devit m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, Sol kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúDevit, nan otarim, n…® uab…® na m…®gei, a?‚Äù Egha Sol pamtem aziava arai. 
\p  
\v 17 Egha a kamagh…®n Devit m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® gumazir arazir aghuim gamim, ez…® k…® gumazir bar kuram. Guizbang…®ra, n…® deragha na gami, ez…® k…® deragha n…® ikarazir puvat…®gha, bar arazir kuram…®n n…® gami.  
\v 18 N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n deragha na geghara ghaze, Ikiav…®ra Itir God na isa n…®n agharim gat…®, ez…® n…® na m…®soghezir puvat…®. Bar guizbang…®ra, n…® arazir kam…®n na gami.  
\v 19 K…® fo, gumazitam uan apanim gas…®ghas…®ghamin tuavim ik…®va, a tizim bagh aneteght…®ma a pura mangam? Puvat…®gham. Ez…® n…® arazir kam gami, kamagh amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar deraghv…®ra n…® damuva deraghv…®ra n…® ikaragham.  
\v 20 K…® kamagh…®n bar fo, n…® Israelian atrivim…®n ikiam. Egh n…® gavgavigh deraghv…®ra kantrin kam gativaght…®, n…®n ovavir boriba uaghan a gativagh mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
