\v 22 Ez…® Devit akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam gami. Ez…® Sol uamategha uan nguibam…®n zuima, Devit uan adarazi ko uamategha uan m…®sozir danganir gavgavir moga itim…®n ghue. 
\c 25  
\s1 Samuel areme 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Samuel aremez…®ma, Israelian gumazamiziba bar iza uari akuvagha a bagha azi. Egha me Raman nguibar ekiam…®n, an d…®penim…®n m…®riam…®n anefa. 
\p Samuel…®n ovevem…®n g…®n, Devit uan gumaziba ko d…®kavigha ghua, Paran…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n iti. 
\s1 Abigel Devit…®n akura 
\p  
\v 2-3 Dughiar kam…®n, Maon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazir mam, an ziam Nabal, a Kalep…®n ik…®zim…®n ovavir boribar gumazir mam. A Karmel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n nguazir mam…®n iti. A dag…®ar av…®riba itir gumazir mam, egha 3,000plan sipsipba ko 1,000pla memeba iti. An amuim…®n ziam, Abigel, an amizir bar dirim, a n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ko fofozir aghuiba iti. Ez…® Nabal adaribagh amir gumazim, an araziba ikufi. 
\p Dughiar kam…®n, Nabal Karmel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikia, uan sipsipbar ar…®zibar ghori.  
\v 4 Ez…® Devit gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikia orazima, Nabal ingangarir kam gami.  
\v 5 Ez…® a gumazir 10plan igiaba amadaz…®ma, me Nabal bagha Karmel…®n zui. A kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Karmel…®n mang…® nan ziam…®n dughiar aghuim is…® Nabal dan…®ngigh.  
\v 6 Ia kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòDevit ghaze, O nan namakam, k…® kamagh…®n God…®n azai, a n…® ko n…®n ik…®zim ko n…®n biziba bar, navir am…®rizim ko dabirabir aghuim is…® ia dan…®ngam.  
\v 7 Devit kamagh…®n oraki, gumazir maba n…®n sipsipbar ar…®zibar ghori. A kamaghsua, n…® deraghv…®ra fogh, n…®n sipsipbagh eghuvir gumaziba, e ko Karmel…®n itima, e arazir kuratam…®n me gamizir puvat…®gha, men bizitam okemezir puvat…®.  
\v 8 N…® men azaraght…®, e n…® geghaniz…® mogh…®ra me n…® geghanam. Dat…®r…®gh…®n isar ekiam…®n dughiam, ez…® Devit n…® bagha e amadaz…®ma e izi. A kamaghsua, n…® en apangkufigh, e mati n…®n ingangarir gumaziba, ez…® n…® mati Devit…®n afeziam. E uari, n…® daghetaba ik…®va, taba e dan…®ngigh.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Devit…®n gumaziba ghua, Devit…®n ziam…®n akar kabar Nabal geghanigha a m…®zua iti.  
\v 10 Ez…® Nabal kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir kam Devit, Jesin otarim, a manmagh…®n garir gumazim? K…® a g…®fozir puvat…®. K…® kamagh…®n oraki, dughiar kabar, ingangarir gumazir k…®nir av…®riba uan gumazir dapanibar aragharui. Devit ti uaghan pura ingangarir gumazir k…®nir mam, egha uaghan aragharuir gumazim.  
\v 11 Ia managh…®ra ize, k…® ia g…®fozir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® uan bretba ko, d…®paba, ko uan ingangarir gumazir nan sipsipbar ar…®ziba aghoreziba, k…® me bagha m…®soghezir as…®zir tuzir taba is…®, ia dan…®ngan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham. K…® aghua.‚Äù 
