\v 12 Ez…® Devit…®n ingangarir gumaziba Nabal…®n akar kam baregha uamategha ghua Devit m…®keme.  
\v 13 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bar mogh…®ra m…®dorozim bagh m…®dorozir sababa inigh uan ogh…®riabar aghuigh, m…®soghs…® mang…®.‚Äù Egha me vaghvagha bar mogh…®ra Devit…®n akam…®n g…®n zuima, Devit uaghan uan m…®dorozir sabam uan ogh…®riam garu. Egha a 400plan gumaziba kamagh me inigha zui. Ez…® 200plan gumaziba, a bizibagh eghuvasa me m…®kemez…®, me iti. 
\p  
\v 14 Dughiar kam…®n Nabal…®n ingangarir gumazir mam ghua, kamagh…®n Nabal…®n amuim Abigel m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDevit gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikia, uan gumazir maba amadaz…® me iza, en gumazir ekiam dughiar aghuim a gan…®ngi. Ez…® a pamtem…®n me dagaragha men atara akar kuram me gan…®ngi.  
\v 15 Gumazir kaba faragha arazir kuratam…®n e gamizir puvat…®. Me zurara arazir aghuibaram e gami. Me zurara e ko dadaba aghuir danganim…®n iti. Me en bizitam okemezir puvat…®.  
\v 16 E me ko ikiava uan sipsipbagh eghuvir dughiam…®n, me arueba ko d…®magariba bar, d…®vazim…®n m…®n e ek…®arugha derav…®ra e geghufi.  
\v 17 N…® deraghv…®ra fogh, Devit uan gumaziba ko iz…®, en gumazir ekiam ko an gumazamizir a ko itibagh as…®ghas…®ghasa n…®ghn…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e n…® bagha izi. E n…®n azai, n…® deraghv…®ra n…®ghn…®gh, n…® manmagh…®n os…®mt…®zir kam ak…®ram? E bar Nabal g…®fo, a gumazir bar kuram, a ifaghata, akaba barazir puvat…®zir gumazim.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Abigel kamagh…®n oregha zuam…®ra 200pla bretba ko memen inim…®n ingarizir wain itir m…®sevir pumuning inigha, sipsip…®n 5plan tuziba ko, 20 kilogrem…®n wit…®n tueziba, ko 100plan wain…®n ov…®zir ik…®zir apuziziba, ko 200pla fik…®n ov…®zir me apuziziba, a dagher kaba bar ada inigha donkibagh is…®n da ar…®ki.  
\v 19 Egha a kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa donkiba inigh faragh mang…®t…®, k…® ian g…®n mangam.‚Äù A bizir amizir kam…®n gun uan pam m…®kemezir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 20 Egha Abigel uan donkin mam gaperagha Devit bativasava tuavir mam…®n zui. Ez…® Devit uaghan tuavir kamra, uan gumaziba ko me munagh an ikegha izi. Ez…® Abigel tuavir kam…®n ghua m…®ghs…®ar mam…®n ak…®rir vuem…®n me bato.  
\v 21 Dughiar kam, Devit n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúK…® tizim bagha gumazir kam…®n biziba gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n dagh eghufi? E an bizitam okemezir pu. Bar puvat…®. An biziba bar deraghav…®ra iti, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n an arazir kuram…®n na ikara, an arazim derazir puvat…®.  
\v 22 Bizir kam bang…®n, k…® d…®magarir kam…®n an adarazir gumaziba bar me kuavaremegham. Puvat…®ght…®ma, k…® God…®n azaraght…®, a na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham.‚Äù\f + \fr 25:22 \ft Bar fom…®ra, me Hibrun akam…®n aven itir akar kam, Grik…®n akam…®n a g…®ra. Ez…® Grik…®n akam ghaze, ‚ÄúGod na m…®sueght…®, k…® aremegham.‚Äù Fofozir gumazir av…®riba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, akar kam, ‚Äúk…® uab…®,‚Äù a uaghan Hibrun akam…®n aven kagh iti. Egha me g…®n ghaze, Devit men atrivir aghuim. Egha me dat…®r…®gh…®n a giragha ghaze, ‚Äúnan apanibara.‚Äù\f* 
\p  
\v 23-24 Ez…® Abigel iza Devit…®n apigha zuam…®ra uan donki gis…®n ikegha faghaf…®ragha, magh…®ra Devit…®n dagarimning…®n borogh…®n ir…®gha, uan guam isa nguazim m…®tuagha ghaze, ‚ÄúO nan gumazir ekiam, kar nan os…®mt…®zimra, n…® os…®mt…®zir kam nan pam dar…®ghan mark…®. K…® n…®n ingangarir amizim, k…® n…® m…®k…®masa. Ga uaning! N…® ti nan akam baragham, o?  
\v 25 Guizbang…®ra, n…® Nabal…®n akabagh n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, an araziba bar ikufi. An ziam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, gumazir onganir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®zim, ez…® an arazim an ziam…®n m…®rara ghu. O nan gumazir ekiam, k…® n…®n ingangarir amizim, n…® e bagha amadazir gumazir igiaba, k…® uab…® men ganizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 26 N…® oragh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® n…® gamiz…® gumazir n…®n apanim gamiba, n…® uab…® me m…®soghezir puvat…®. Puvat…®z…®, men ghuzibar os…®mt…®zim n…®n ikiam. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n zurara itim…®n ziam…®n, k…® guizbang…®ra pamtem…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, m…®zazir God Nabal dan…®ngamim, a uaghan n…®n apaniba kamagh…®ra me damuam. 
\p  
\v 27 ‚ÄúNan gumazir ekiam, k…® n…®n ingangarir amizim, nan ifongiam kamak…®n, n…® nan bizir aghuir k…® n…® gan…®diba inigh, uan ingangarir gumazir n…®n g…®n zuibar an…®ng.  
\v 28 Ga uaning, k…® n…®n ingangarir amizim, k…® n…®n damazim…®n arazir kuratam damight…®, n…® nan arazir kuram g…®n amadagh. Nan gumazir ekiam, k…® fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® amadaz…®, n…® an ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua an apanibav sosi. K…® God…®n azai, n…® nguazir kam…®n ikiamin dughiam…®n, n…® arazir kuratam damighan kogham. Kamagh amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® damight…® n…® atrivim…®n otogham, eght…® g…®n n…®n ovavir boriba Israelian atrivibar otiv mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\p  
\v 29 ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, gumazitaba n…®n g…®nt…®gh n…®n m…®soghs…® iz…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God deraghv…®ra n…®n akurvagham, mati gumazim uan bizir aghuiba deraghav…®ra dagh eghufi. Egh n…®n apaniba batuegham, mati gumazim katapel…®n dag…®am gasavamadi mogh…®n, a n…®n apanibagh as…®vamangam.  
\v 30 Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, a bizir aghuir av…®riba n…® dan…®ngam, egh n…® damight…® n…® Israelia en atrivim…®n ikiam.  
\v 31 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, nan pam m…®soghan mark…®. Nan gumazir ekiam, n…® uab…® gumazitam puram a m…®soghez…®, an aremezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, men ghuzibar os…®mt…®zitam n…®n dafarimning…®n ikian kogham. Ga uaning, k…® n…®n ingangarir amizim, k…® kamagh…®n n…®n azai, Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®n deraghv…®ra n…® damut…®, n…® na gin…®r…®gh deraghv…®ra na damu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 32 Ez…® Devit akar kaba baregha kamagh…®n Abigel m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelia en God, a n…® amadaz…® n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n iza na bato, bizir kam bang…®n k…® an ziam fe.  
\v 33 N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nan anogoroke, ez…® k…® Nabal…®n os…®mt…®zim bagha, uan dafarimning…®n gumazir tabav soghez…® me ariaghirezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, men ghuzibar os…®mt…®zim nan itir puvat…®. Bizir kam bang…®n, k…® n…®n akaba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba bagha God m…®naba.  
\v 34 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia gas…®ghas…®ghan nan anogoroke. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n zurara itim, a Israelian God, k…® an ziam…®n guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…® ti na bagha zuam…®ra izezir puvat…®z…®, gurumzaraghan Nabal…®n ingangarir gumazitam angam…®ra ikeghan koghai.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 35 Egha Devit bizir Abigel inigha izeziba inigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® dat…®r…®gh…®n uamategh uan d…®penim…®n mang…®va navim am…®ragh ik…®. K…® n…®n akaba baregha g…®fa. N…® na m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, k…® Nabal amizir arazir kuram g…®n amadagh, ia m…®sueghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 36 Ez…® Abigel uamategha d…®penim…®n ghugha Nabal…®n garima, an atriviba amir isar ekiabar m…®n isam gami. Egha a bar akongegha wain…®n d…®par av…®rim apava bar ongani. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Abigel bizitam…®n gun a geghanizir puvat…®gha ghua am…®mzaraghan.  
\v 37 Ez…® am…®nim tiraz…®ma, Nabal…®n n…®ghn…®zim uamategha izi, ez…® an amuim Abigel iza bizir otivizibar gun a geghari. Nabal oregha g…®vagha, bar zuam…®ra an d…®ghorim an koz…®, a ir…®gha m…®k…®r…®, egha a mati dag…®am pura ir…®ghav iti.  
\v 38 Egha a kamagh…®ra ir…®ghav ikia ghua 10plan dughiaba g…®vaz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Nabal m…®soghez…®ma an areme. 
\p  
