\v 5 Me iza Devit m…®kemez…®, Devit d…®kavigha ghua Sol itir averpenibar ghu, egha a bar deraghav…®ra Sol uan m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim Apner ko, aning akuir danganim…®n gari, Apner a Ner…®n otarim. Sol uan averpenibar tong…®rama akuima, an m…®dorozir gumaziba an okarigha akui.  
