\v 19 Kamagh…®n amiz…® atrivim, n…® nan gumazir ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n ifonge, n…® na barakigh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® na m…®soghs…®, n…® m…®kemeght…®, k…® a bagh ofa tam damight…®, a nan apangkuvigham. Eght…® gumaziba na m…®soghs…® n…®n navim ginivt…®, gumazir kaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God me gas…®ghas…®gham. Guizbang…®ra, me kamaghsua, me kantrin kam…®n na batueght…®, k…® mang…®va asebar tevimning ap…®r…®va men ziaba fam. Eght…® bizir aghuir Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan gumazamiziba bagha an…®diba, k…® da inian kogham.  
