\v 2 Egha Devit uan 600plan gumaziba ko me gumazim Akis bagha zui, a Maok…®n otarim, a Get…®n nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim.  
\v 3 Ez…® Devit uan gumaziba ko men amuiroghboriba, me Atrivim Akis ko Get…®n apiaghav iti. Devit…®n amuir pumuning a ko iti. Mam…®n ziam Ahinoam, a Jesril…®n amizim, ez…® igharazim Abigel, a Karmelian amizim, a faragha ikezir pam Nabal, an areme.  
