\v 3 \x - \xo 28:3 \xt Ofa Gami 20:27; God…®n Araziba 18:10-11; 1 Samuel 25:1\x*Samuel fom…®ra aremez…®ma, Israelia a bagha azigha, an nguibar ekiam Raman anefa. Dughiar kam…®n, Sol oveaghuezibar duaba ko m…®geir gumazamiziba batozima, me ua Israel…®n kantrin itir puvat…®. 
