\v 20 Ez…® Sol akar kam baregha bar atiatigha, magh…®ra ir…®gha nguazim gir…®ghav ti. An aruer kam ko d…®magarir kam…®n daghetam amezir puvat…®gha, gavgaviba bar puvat…®.  
\v 21 Ez…® amizir kam ghua Sol…®n garima, a bar atiatingi, ez…® a kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam n…® oragh, k…® n…®n ingangarir amizim, k…® n…®n akam…®n g…®n ghua, kamagh…®n uab…® g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, k…® ovengam o k…® angam…®ra ikiam. K…® n…® baregha bizir kam gami.  
