\p  
\v 6 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Atrivim Akis Devit…®n diagha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n zurara itim…®n ziam…®n, k…® guizbang…®ra kamagh…®n n…® m…®gei, n…® gumazir aghuim ez…® k…® ghaze, kamagh…®n ti deragham, n…® na ko iz…® m…®dorozir kam…®n en akuragh. N…® na bagha izezir dughiam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, k…® n…®n arazir kuratam…®n apizir puvat…®. Ez…® atrivir igharaziba kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® e ko mangan kogham.  
\v 7 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® navir am…®rizim sara uamategh nguibam…®n mang…® deraghv…®ra daperagh. N…® bizir Filistian atriviba ifongezir puvat…®zibar amut…®, me n…® bas…®mam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n Atrivim Akis m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan gumazir ekiam, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, k…® os…®mt…®zir manam gami? Dughiar k…® iza n…®n ingangarim gamua ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n itim…®n, k…® arazir kurar manam gami? Atrivim, bizir tizim bagh k…® mang…® n…®n akuragh n…®n apanibav soghan kogham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Akis kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan damazim…®n mati, God…®n ensel…®n mam, egha os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazibar dapaniba m…®kemegha g…®fa, n…® e ko m…®dorozim bagh mangan kogham.  
\v 10 Devit, n…® oragh. Gurumzaraghan am…®nim magh tit…®ma, n…® uan m…®dorozir gumazir igharaziba ko, ia d…®kavigh biziba ak…®r. Am…®nim angazangart…® ia deragh gan…®va, d…®kavigh uamategh nguibar k…® n…® gan…®ngizim…®n mang…®. K…® bar n…® gifonge, kamagh…®n amiz…® n…® na bas…®man mark…®.‚Äù\f + \fr 29:10 \ft Vez…®n kam…®n aven, akar maba Hibrun akam…®n itir puvat…®. Da kamak…®n, ‚Äúnguibar k…® n…® gan…®ngizim…®n mang…®. K…® bar n…® gifonge, kamagh…®n amiz…® n…® na bas…®man mark…®.‚Äù Akar kaba ti fom…®ra iti, egha g…®n ovenge. Ez…® akar kaba ikiav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, gumazir maba Grik…®n akam…®n da g…®ra, ez…® akar kaba Grik…®n akam…®n 1 Samuel…®n iti.\f* 
\p  
\v 11 Kamagh…®n amiz…® Devit bar m…®zaraghara uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me ua kantri Filistian ghuez…®, Filistiaba me Jesril…®n ghue. 
\c 30  
\s1 Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua Amalekia m…®sosi 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me 3plan dughiabar arua ghua, uan nguibam Siklak…®n oto. Me garima, a ikuvigha g…®fa. Dughiar Devit Filistiabar m…®dorozir gumaziba ko itim…®n, Amalekia iza Judan saut…®n amadaghan Negev…®n itir nguibar dozibar m…®soghasa izi. Me uaghan Siklak…®n nguibam m…®sogha, uari bagh an biziba inigha nguibam gaboroz…®ma a isi.  
\v 2 Egha me Siklak…®n amiziba bar me inigha ghue, guivir igiabar ikegha ghua amizir ghuriba sara, Amalekia me m…®soghezir puvat…®gha pura me inigha ghue. 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Devit g…®n uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua Siklak…®n otogha garima, nguibam sigha g…®fa. Me kamagh…®n fo, Amalekia Devit ko an m…®dorozir gumazibar amuiba ko boriba bar me inigha ghue.  
\v 4 Ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me bar puv…®rama azia ghua men gavgaviba bar g…®fa.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 30:5 \xt 1 Samuel 25:42-43\x*Devit…®n amuimning, Ahinoam ko Abigel, Amalekia uaghan aning inigha ghu. Ahinoam, a Jesrilian amizim, ez…® Abigel, a Karmelian amizim, a faragha ikezir pam Nabal, an areme. 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Devit…®n gumaziba uan otariba ko guivibagh n…®ghn…®gha, bar a basemegha dag…®abar a ginivight…® an aremeghasava amima, a bar os…®mt…®zir ekiam isi. Egha Devit uan God ko m…®gei, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gavgavim an n…®ghn…®zim gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 30:7 \xt 1 Samuel 22:20-23\x*Ez…® Devit Ahimelek…®n otarim Abiatar…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúOfa gamir gumazibar korotiar otevir azenan azuir kam, n…® a inigh iz…®t…®, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n n…®ghn…®zim g…®foka.‚Äù Ez…® Abiatar korotiar kam inigha izi. 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azara, ‚ÄúK…® mang…®va ok…®mak…®ar gumazir kabar ag…®ragham, o markiam? K…® mang…® men apigham o?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® men ag…®ragh. N…® mang…® me batogh me m…®sogh…®va, uan amuiba ko boriba ua me inigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9-10 Kamagh…®n amiz…® Devit uan 600plan gumaziba ko ghua Amalekian ag…®ra. Me ghua Besor…®n Fanem…®n otogha, men marazi daruan ibura. Men m…®karziba men am…®raz…® me d…®pam ab…®ghan iburagha magh…®ra iti. Men d…®bobonim 200…®n borogh…®n tu. Ez…® Devit 400plan gumaziba ko, Amalekian g…®n zui. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Devit…®n m…®dorozir gumazir maba danganir k…®nir mam abigha ghua Isip…®n gumazir igiar mam…®n apigha, a inigha Devit bagha ghua, dagheba ko d…®pam a gan…®ngi.  
\v 12 Egha me figh…®n ik…®zir muziarir apuzizir mam ko wain…®n ov…®zir apuzizir ik…®zir pumuning a gan…®ngi. Ana aruer 3pla ko d…®magarir 3plan dagheba ko d…®patam amezir puvat…®gha, m…®tiriam bang…®n m…®k…®r…®gha, gavgaviba bar puvat…®. An amegha g…®vagha ua gavgavim ini.  
\v 13 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúTina n…®n gumazir ekiam? Egha a nguibar manam…®n gumazim?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Isipian gumazim, egha k…® Amalekian gumazim…®n ingangarir gumazir mam. K…® areima, nan gumazir ekiam kagh na at…®z…®, k…® kagh itima dughiar 3pla g…®fa.  
\v 14 E kantri Judan saut…®n amadaghan Negev…®n danganim…®n ghua, Judaba ko Keretia ko Kalepian m…®sogha men biziba bar ada ini. Egha e Siklak…®n ghua men nguibar kam gaboroz…®ma a isi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Devit kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúN…® na inigh ok…®mak…®ar gumazir kaba bagh mangam, o?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® a ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, ga mangam. Ez…® k…® kamaghsua, n…® God…®n ziam…®n akar gavgavim ak…®righ suam, n…® na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeghan kogham, egh uaghan na is…® nan gumazir ekiam…®n dafarim dar…®ghan mark…®. N…® kamagh…®n damight…®, k…® n…® inigh mangam.‚Äù Ez…® Devit a ko akar gavgavim ak…®ri. 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Isipian gumazir kam Devit inigha Amalekia bagha ghu. Dughiar kam…®n, Amalekia bizir av…®rir Filistian kantri ko Judan nguazim…®n iniziba bagha isar ekiam gamua, dagheba ko d…®par onganiba apava tintinibar nguazim gireghav iti.  
\v 17 Ez…® Devit uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me Amalekia bararkia ghua am…®nim magh kuigha izima, me ghua m…®dorozim fore. Egha Amalekian m…®sogha ghua bar guarat…®zim…®n tu. Egha Amalekian av…®ribav soghez…®ma me ariaghire. 400plan gumazibara uan kamelbagh apiagha are. Ez…® igharaziba bar mogh…®ra ariaghire.  
\v 18 Ez…® Devit uan amuimning ko amizir igharaziba ko boriba ko men bizir Amalekia iniziba bar uam ada ini.  
\v 19 Men bizir ekiaba ko bizir muziariba bar iti, bizitam ikuvizir puvat…®. Egha an m…®dorozir gumazibar otariba ko guiviba, ko bizir apaniba okemeziba bar, Devit bar mogh…®ra ua da ini.  
\v 20 Egha Devit Amalekian bulmakauba ko sipsipba bar ada ini. Ez…® an m…®dorozir gumaziba da inigha men faragha zui. Ez…® gumazamiziba arazir kam…®n gara kamagh…®n d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar, Devit…®n as…®zibara, a m…®dorozim…®n da ini.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Egha me ghuava, men 200plan gumaziba Besor…®n Fanem…®n me bato. Kar gumazir faragha m…®karziba am…®ragha d…®pam ab…®ghan iburaziba, Devit me ataghiz…®, me a m…®zua kagh iti. Ez…® gumazir kaba dat…®r…®gh…®n iza Devit ko an gumazamiziba bato, ez…® Devit men borogh…®n ghua dughiar aghuim me gan…®ngi.  
\v 22 M…®dorozir gumazir Devit ko ghuez…® maba, me gumazir aghuiba puvat…®, me ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir e ko ghua m…®soghezir puvat…®zir kaba, me e m…®sogha inizir biziba inian kogham. Me uan amuiba ko boribara inigh pura mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Ez…® Devit ghaze, ‚ÄúBar puvat…®gham. Nan aveghbuaba, ia m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kabar amuan mark…®. Ia fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® bizir kaba e gan…®ngi. A uab…® e geghuva en akuraz…®, e apanir en nguibam gas…®ghas…®ghiziba ab…®nigha bizir kaba ini.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 30:24 \xt D…®boboniba 31:27; Josua 22:8\x*Tinara ian akaba baragham? Puvat…®gham. E deraghv…®ra biziba ab…®gh, gumaziba vaghvagh iniamin biziba vorogh…®ra me dan…®ngam. Gumazir en bizibagh eghuviba ko gumazir m…®dorozim bagha ghueziba, me iniamin biziba bar vorogh…®ra mang…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Arazir kam, Devit arazir God ifongezim ko bizir a damuasa me m…®kemezim…®n m…®n, Israelia bagha a gami. Ez…® Israelia zurara akar kam…®n g…®n ghua, iza dat…®r…®gh…®n ikiav…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 26 Egha Devit uamategha Siklak…®n ghugha, m…®dorozim…®n inizir bizir maba isa uan namakar mabagh an…®di, me Judan gumazir dapaniba. A kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar ian bizir aghuir Amalekia okemeziba, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n apaniba da bizir aghuir av…®riba ini, egha maba ia gan…®di.‚Äù  
\v 27 Devit bizir aghuir kaba isa nguibar ekiar kabagh an…®di: Betel, ko Rama, a Judan saut…®n amadaghan Negev…®n itir danganim…®n ko Jatir,  
\v 28 ko Aroer, Sipmot, Estemoa,  
\v 29 ko Rakal Jeramelia ko Kinian nguibaba,  
\v 30 ko Horma ko Borasan ko Atak,  
\v 31 ko Hebron. Bizir maba, Devit fom…®ra uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko aruizir nguibaba, a bar mogh…®ra bizir aghuiba me gan…®ngi. 
\c 31  
\s1 Sol uan otariba ko ariaghire 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n, Filistiaba ghua Israelia ko m…®sogha, Gilboan m…®ghs…®am…®n Israelian gumazir av…®ribav soghez…®ma me ariaghire. Ez…® men marazi m…®dorozim ategha are.  
\v 2 Ez…® Sol uan otariba ko, me uaghan are, ez…® Filistiaba men ag…®ragha ghua me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Sol…®n otaribar ziabar kara: Jonatan, Abinadap ko Malkisua.  
\v 3 Ez…® m…®dorozim bar ekevez…®ma gumaziba Sol…®n ag…®ra. Filistian maba an apigha barir pibar a gasima, barir maba an m…®tiviz…®, a bar amughamuki. 
\p  
\v 4 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Sol uan gumazir igiar an m…®dorozir biziba aterim…®n diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uan m…®dorozir sabam inigh iz…® na b…®raght…®ma k…® aremeka. Puvat…®ght…®, Filistian m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghorezir puvat…®zir kaba, iz…® na d…®pov m…®zazim na dan…®ng…®va na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir igiar kam bar atiatigha Sol ginivan bar aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Sol uab…® uan m…®dorozir sabam asaragha a gaveraz…®, sabam a m…®t…®z…® an areme.  
\v 5 Ez…® gumazir igiar kam gari Sol aremez…®, a uaghan uan m…®dorozir sabam asaragha a gaveraz…®, sabam a m…®t…®z…® a uaghan Sol ko areme.  
\v 6 Dughiar kamra, Sol uan otarir 3pla ko, an gumazir igiar an m…®dorozir biziba aterim ko, Sol…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba sara, me bar mogh…®ra ariaghire. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Israelian Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n itiba, ko Jesril…®n danganir zarim…®n vong…®n itiba kamagh…®n oraki, Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba are. Me uaghan kamagh…®n oraki, Sol uan otariba ko, me bar ariaghire, ez…® me uan nguibar ekiaba ategha are. Ez…® g…®n Filistiaba iza nguibar kaba inigha dar iti. 
\p  
\v 8 M…®dorozim g…®vaz…®, am…®mzaraghan Filistiaba uamategha iza, Israelian ariaghirezibar kuabar korotiaba suva, men biziba iniasa izi. Egha me garima, Sol uan otariba ko, men kuaba Gilboan m…®ghs…®am…®n ireghav iti.  
\v 9 Ez…® me Sol…®n kuam…®n f…®rim atugha, an m…®dorozir korotiaba ini. Egha me gumazir maba amadaz…®ma, me akaba isa ghua Filistiabar nguazim…®n tintinibar arua uan asebar d…®penibar aven ghua an gun gumazamizibav gei.  
\v 10 Egha me Sol…®n m…®dorozir korotiaba isa uan aser amizim Astarten d…®penim gat…®. Egha me Sol ko an otaribar kuaba inigha ghua, Betsan nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazim…®n me gui. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Israelian Jabes…®n nguibar ekiam…®n iti darasi, me Gileat…®n nguazim…®n aven iti, me Filistiaba Sol gamizir arazim…®n eghaghanim baraki.  
\v 12 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Jabes…®n m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba d…®mangan d…®kavigha ghua Betsan oto. Me ghua nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazim…®n, Sol ko an otarir 3plan kuaba inigha iza Jabes…®n da tuez…® da isi.  
\v 13 Egha me Sol ko an otaribar aghariba inigha, ghua Jabes…®n nguibar ekiam…®n temer povir mam…®n da isa mozim gat…®. Egha me bar mogh…®ra me bagha aziava osemegha 7plan dughiabar me bagha dagheba ataki.